\id ROM - Akawaio New Testament Translation Project
\h RON
\toc1 Kareta Paarʉ Nennoko'pʉ Ron Pon Kon Ena'
\toc2 Ron
\toc3 Ron
\mt2 Kareta Paarʉ Nennoko'pʉ
\mt1 Ron Pon Kon
\mt2 Ena'
\imt1 Ekamanin
\ip \bk Kareta Paarʉ Nennoko'pʉ Ron Pon Kon Ena'\bk* e'menuka'pʉ, tʉutɨ e'ma ta' to' ekonekato' pe iye'kuu'pʉ rʉ'pʉ tʉutɨto' pe so'si Ron po na'ne' pona. Iyekonekato' esi'pʉ te'tʉrawasomato' pe Kʉri'san amʉ' koro'tau mɨrɨ yau aka'ne' pe rɨ, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ to' uya tʉpika'tɨi' tʉutɨto' pe Sʉ'pen pona. Imenuka'pʉ iya Kʉri'san amʉ' uya apurɨto' to'ka'nʉkʉ tʉuya ekamanin pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Kʉri'san amʉ' uko'manto' tenpoikai' ɨnku'pai te'to' rɨ. Kareta yau iyenuka'sa' pe inekamanʉ itekareei esi.
\ip Miyarɨ ta tʉpo ka'pon amʉ' so'si tawon kon Ron pon kon pɨ' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ to' pana'tɨ tʉpo to' pona tʉwɨpʉremato' pɨ', Paarʉ uya ekama tʉkaretaai yau tʉusauro'to' ipɨ': “Itekare uya enpoika Papa uya ka'pon amʉ' konekato' tʉpokon pe: Apurɨto' poro iyepiya'tɨ'pʉ si'kɨrɨ iu'matʉ pʉ'kʉ pona” (1:17).
\ip Paarʉ uya nin si serɨ tʉusauro'to' ipɨ' emo'ka. Tanporo ka'pon amʉ', asa'rɨ rɨ Esuwerʉ amʉ' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen, ekonekato' pe iyesi Papa pokon pe, apʉne pʉra tanporo rɨ ɨsi'kaisarɨ rɨ makoi meruntɨrʉ o'no to' esi pɨ'. Ka'pon amʉ' ekoneka Papa pokon pe Sises Kʉrai apurɨto' to' uya poro. Tʉron nɨ, Paarʉ uya ekama emenna' pe uko'man nɨto' Kʉrai ya' tʉwenai' ipokon pe e'nɨto' serɨ si emenna' pe Papa pokon pe e'nɨto' moron nʉ'pʉ pe. Papa pokon pe apurɨnin e'to' esi ewankamanin pʉra mɨrɨpan emo'ka Papa A'kwarʉ winɨ makoi mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ uma'tan nɨto' meruntɨrʉ apai. Isa'ta 5—8 yau Paarʉ rɨ marɨ uya ekama usaurokʉ Papa iwano' main e'to' mɨrɨto' tukai', mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Papa A'kwarʉ meruntɨrʉ pɨ' apurɨnin pe te'sen uko'manto' yau. Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ itekare ekamai' enno'sa' e'kaai'ma a'toman nɨto' pokon pe mɨrɨ kasa Esuwerʉ amʉ' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen epata'tɨ ka'pon amʉ' iwano' pe Papa nʉkonekanʉ ya' tawon pokon pe. Iye'nonka Sises ewaruma'tɨto' Esuwerʉ amʉ' uya esi, Papa ekonekasa' pe rɨ tanporo ka'pon amʉ' ne'nin pe Papa uya wakʉ nonkato' Sises Kʉrai yau eporo to' uya poken, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ apurɨ iya tɨwɨrɨ rɨ Esuwerʉ amʉ' uya Sises ewaruma'tɨ pen tukai'.
\ip Iu'matʉ pe Paarʉ uya imenuka se kasa Kʉri'san pe e'nɨ uko'manto' esi tukai', tʉusi'nʉnkai' tʉron kon pokon pe e'nɨto' pɨ'. Anʉnpɨtʉ iya tʉusauro'to' ipɨ' ton pe Papa apiyo' pe e'nɨto' pɨ', pata esanon pɨ' tʉtʉrawasooi kon ku'to' Kʉri'san amʉ' uya pɨ', mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨsitonpa pe te'to' ku'to' pɨ', mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ewan wannɨ uya i'tun nɨto' pɨ' uta'toman nɨto'. Tʉkaretaai i'ma'ka iya tekareei ton ke rɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Papa apurɨpɨ'to' main ke.
\iot Iyawon Ekamanin
\io1 Ekamanin mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ isauro'to' ipɨ' (1:1-17)
\io1 Epika'tɨn nɨto' i'se kuru e'nɨto' (1:18—3:20)
\io1 Papa eseru epika'tɨn nɨto' pɨ' (3:21—4:25)
\io1 Emenna' pe uko'man nɨto' Kʉrai yau (5:1—8:39)
\io1 Esuwerʉ Papa ekonekato' yau (9:1—11:36)
\io1 Kʉri'san pe e'nɨ e'to' (12:1—15:13)
\io1 Iye'nonkato' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉmɨrɨ pe miyarɨ tato' iya (15:14—16:27)
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Paarʉ, Sises Kʉrai poitorʉ, esa'sa' itekare ekamai' enno'sa' pe, imo'kasa' wakʉ Papa ekareei iwano' pe, winɨpaino.
\v 2 Serɨ itekare ikupʉ uya tukai' isaurokʉ'pʉ rʉ'pʉ pena pu'kena' amʉ' imaimu pe tʉusauro'san poro Wakʉ iye'menukasa' itekare yau
\v 3 tʉmu pɨ', ka'pon pe te'to' yau Tepi' pa rʉ'pʉ pe na'ne'.
\v 4 Wakʉ pe te'sen Iya'kwarʉ poro ekamasa' rʉ'pʉ meruntɨ ke Papa Mu pe\f + \fr 1:4 \fq ekamasa' rʉ'pʉ meruntɨ ke Papa Mu pe; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq ekamasa' rʉ'pʉ tʉmeruntɨrʉ ke Papa Mu pe\f* iye'mʉ'sa'ka winɨ iyerikʉ'pʉ apai: Sises Kʉrai si uyepuru kon.
\v 5 Iporo mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ itese' iwano' pe wakʉ nonkasa' eposa' man innennoko'san pe e'nɨto' pe, ka'pon amʉ' ne'nin pe e'nɨto' pe Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen koro'tapai imaimu awɨron pe to' e'to' pe apurɨto' to' uya winɨ.
\v 6 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨmɨrɨ'nokon nɨ nɨrɨ si esi kamoro Sises Kʉrai iwano' pe ikɨ'masa' kon koro'tau.
\p 
\v 7 Tanporon kon Ron pon kon enakan Papa ni'nʉnkanʉ ton mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ikɨ'masa' kon wakʉ ton pe to' e'to' pe:
\p Wakʉ nonkasa' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉusewankamai' pʉra ɨwe'to' kon Papa, ukʉipʉnʉ kon mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Itepuru Sises Kʉrai winon nesii ɨyenakan kon pe.
\s1 Paarʉ E'to' Ron Pona Ɨtɨpai
\p 
\v 8 Wapiya, Papa pɨ' tenki ta uya Sises Kʉrai poro tanporo ɨmɨrɨ'nokon pɨ', apʉne pʉra apurɨto' auya'nokon usekare'tɨsa' tanporo non emʉ' kaisa rɨ.
\v 9 Papa, iyapiyo' pe e'to' tanporo uyewan a'kɨrɨ Imu ekareei wakʉ ekama uya yau, esi uyekamanin pe inke rɨ uyenu yau ɨkupʉ uya 'nokon
\v 10 ɨpʉrema yau tɨwɨrɨ rɨ; mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨpʉrema si serɨ pe rɨ Papa eseru awɨrɨ ite'ma uta'kokasa' e'to' pe ɨpiya'nokon utɨto' pe.
\p 
\v 11 Ɨyenpai'nokon esi ɨpika'tɨto' kon pe uya iya'kwarʉ nʉtʉrʉnʉ eponin pe, pana' pe ɨku'nin kon pe—
\v 12 mɨrɨ si, ɨmɨrɨ'nokon mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ urɨ uya apurɨto' winɨ epori'mapɨ'nɨto' pe asa' ipɨ'.
\v 13 I'tunin nan pe pʉra ɨwesi kon i'se pʉra esi, utonpa ton, ekonepɨtʉ'pʉ inke rɨ ɨpiya'nokon utɨto' pe (e'tane mɨrɨ namai' uwa'kʉ'pɨ'sa' serɨ pona rɨ nin si) ɨ'koro'tau'nokon iyakʉ'pʉsa' anʉnto' pe uya, tʉron kon Papa pʉnon kon koro'tau eporo'pʉ uya kasa.\x - \xo 1:13 \xt Inkupʉ'pʉ 19:21\x*
\p 
\v 14 E'nonkasa' pe rɨ esi asa'ron kon ena' Kiri' amʉ' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Kiri' amʉ' pen nɨ ena', asa'rɨ rɨ emepoke' ton mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ emepo pʉnon kon ena'.
\v 15 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', wakʉ itekare ɨnekamapai kuru esi serɨ ɨmɨrɨ'nokon Ron pon kon pɨ' rɨ marɨ.
\p 
\v 16 Wakʉ itekare pɨ' ɨpiyɨtʉ pen nɨ, apʉne pʉra Papa meruntɨrʉ pe iyesi tanporon kon apurɨnin nan epika'tɨto' ike pe; wapiya Esuwerʉ iwano' pe, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Esuwerʉ pen iwano' pe.\x - \xo 1:16 \xt Ma' 8:38\x*
\v 17 Apʉne pʉra wakʉ itekare yau Papa uya anʉn nɨ ipokena' rɨ tukai' apurɨto' winɨ iyepiya'tɨ si'kɨrɨ iu'matʉ pona,\f + \fr 1:17 \fq iyepiya'tɨ si'kɨrɨ iu'matʉ pona; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq apurɨto' apai apurɨto' pona\f* iye'menukasa' na'ne' kasa: “Ipokena' awɨrɨ te'sen uko'mamʉ apurɨto' winɨ,”\f + \fr 1:17 \ft Apa'ka' 2:4\f* tawon.
\s1 Ka'pon Kota'mato' Papa Uya
\p 
\v 18 Papa uya kota'man nɨto' usenpoikasa' Epʉn poi Papa pʉra e'nɨto' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨri ka'pon amʉ' eseru pɨ' wakʉ i'tuto' pe pʉra iku'nin nan ɨri teseru kon winɨ,
\v 19 Papa i'tuto' ipɨ' esi to' pona tense rɨ, apʉne pʉra tense rɨ Papa uya iku'sa' to' pona.
\v 20 Apʉne pʉra non e'kaa'pʉ si'kɨrɨ Papa ewakiri tʉusensen pen—siyaro' rɨ imeruntɨrʉ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Papa pe iye'to' i'naino rɨ—usensa' wakʉ pe rɨ, tʉto'ka'nʉ'se iyekonekasa' rʉ'pʉ winɨ, ka'pon amʉ' e'to' pe iye'wapu'tɨto' ipona pʉra.
\p 
\v 21 Apʉne pʉra Papa i'tu tane to' uya, Papa pe to' uya apurɨpɨtʉ pʉra iyesi, to' uya tenki ta pʉra rɨ iyesi ipɨ', e'tane to' usenuminkato' esi iwotori'pɨ pʉra rɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ emepo pʉn to' ewan ewarumamʉ'pʉ.\x - \xo 1:21 \xt E'pe'sas 4:17-18\x*
\v 22 Emepoke' pe to' e'ku'tane, epe' rɨ to' ena'pʉ,
\v 23 mɨrɨpan kon uya Papa teri'sen pen ku'to' eke pe entakanoma'pʉ to' uya ipe iye'to' pe ika'sa' ke ka'pon teri'sen pe rɨ nin mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ toron amʉ' pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ o' amʉ' pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ene amʉ' rɨ.\x - \xo 1:23 \xt Isu'taronomi 4:16-18\x*
\p 
\v 24 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', Papa uya to' nonkasa' ɨri to' ewan e'to' i'se yau ɨri pe tekumato' kon yau tʉtonpa kon pokon pe tʉpun kon eno'mato' to' uya ya'.
\v 25 I'nairon pe Papa e'to' entakanoma to' uya kasi pe e'nɨto' ke, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ika'sa' ton nɨ apurɨpɨtʉ to' uya mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ iyapiyo' pe rɨ to' esi ika'nin nʉ'pʉ ta pe pʉra rɨ—tɨwɨrɨ rɨ tapurɨpɨ'sen. Amen.
\p 
\v 26 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', Papa uya to' nonkasa' piyɨ'nʉ'nin nɨ nɨkɨ eseru ya'. To' uri'samo ton nɨ uya i'naino pe rɨ e'nɨto' entakanoma i'naino pen nɨ ke.
\v 27 Mɨrɨ kasa rɨ marɨ, warawoti'si amʉ' uya i'naino uri'san pokon pe e'nɨto' nonkasa', mɨrɨpan kon a'mintasa' tʉnɨkɨru kon yau tʉtonpa kon pɨ'. Warawoti'si amʉ' uya ɨri rɨ kuu'pʉ warawoti'si amʉ' pokon pe, mɨrɨpan kon uya tekota'mato' kon eposa' tʉpun kon yau iye'to' awɨrɨ pʉra te'sa' kon wenai.
\p 
\v 28 Miyarɨ rɨ, to' usenuminka kasa pʉra rɨ Papa i'tunin pe e'nɨto' enkurunpanin pe, to' nonkasa' iya iye'to' awɨrɨ pʉra to' usenuminkato' ya', tʉku'sen pen nɨ ku'to' pe to' uya.
\v 29 To' rɨ si epe'tɨsa' tanporon nɨ ɨri eseru ke, ɨri ke, mentai e'nɨto' ke mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ iteseru pe te'sen awɨrɨ pʉra e'nɨto' ike ke. Ɨri pe tʉron kon pɨ' te'ku'san pe to' esi, te'wɨsan pe, ɨsipɨ' te'san pe, enku'tɨnin nan pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨri ɨnku'pai te'san pe. Ka'pon eseru pɨ' tʉusauro'san pe,
\v 30 ɨri pe ka'pon pɨ' tʉusauro'san pe, Papa ewaruma'tɨnin nan pe, sapemanin nan pe, i'tunin pe te'ku'san pe, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉutapurɨsan pe; ɨri kupʉ eseru sara'tɨnin nan pe; tʉsan kon maimu awɨron kon pen pe;
\v 31 iya'kwarʉ pʉnon kon pe, apurɨ pokena' ton pen pe, tʉusi'nʉnkasan pen pe, ɨsentu'mʉnon kon pe, aiko tawon nan pen pe.
\v 32 I'tui'ma rɨ Papa usauro'sa' esi ipoken kamoro serɨ rupɨ ku'nin nan esi uma'tan nɨto' eponin nan pe tawon, serɨ ton kuru kupʉ to' uya, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ kamoro serɨ ku'nin nan pɨ' rɨ nɨrɨ wakʉ pe man ta to' uya.
\c 2
\s1 Papa Uya Ipoken Eseru Aimenkato'
\p 
\v 1 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', ɨmɨrɨ, ka'pon, ɨnʉ' rɨ eseru aimenkanin, ɨye'wapu'tɨto' ipona pʉra iyesi, ɨ'rɨ poirɨ rɨ tʉron nɨ eseru aimenka auya, ɨiwano' pe rɨ nin ɨuseno'ma mɨrɨ, apʉne pʉra ɨmɨrɨ eseru aimenkanin uya mɨrɨ ton nɨ kupʉ.\x - \xo 2:1 \xt Ma'siu 7:1; Ʉru' 6:37\x*
\v 2 Serɨ si i'tu'nokon Papa uya eseru aimenkato' esi kamoro serɨ rupɨ ku'nin nan pɨ' esi i'nairon po.
\v 3 Mɨrɨ kasa si ɨmɨrɨ, ka'pon nɨ nin, uya eseru aimenkato' kupʉ a'tai to' pɨ' mɨrɨ rɨ kupʉi'ma, Papa uya eseru aimenkato' piyapai ayainʉmʉ tukai' pe' ɨye'kupʉ?
\v 4 Mɨrɨ pe pʉra katɨ, eke pe rɨ ɨsi'nʉnke' pe iye'to' iku'tane auya, ɨyenpɨ'to' iya, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉuseta'kai' pʉra iye'to' nurunpa auya, i'tui'ma pʉra Papa e'to' ɨsi'nʉnke' pe uya ayato' esi ɨyera'tɨto' ya'?
\p 
\v 5 E'tane apʉne pʉra sa'man pe rɨ tera'tɨsen pe pʉra rɨ ɨyewan esi pɨ', kota'man nɨto' amʉranʉkʉ auya ɨiwano' pe rɨ Papa uya kota'man nɨto' weyu a'taino pe, ipokena' eseru aimenkato' iya usenpoika a'tai.
\v 6 Papa uya, “itʉrʉ ka'pon kaisa rɨ inkupʉ'pʉ pɨ' tense,”\f + \fr 2:6 \ft Eren 62:12; Ipu'ketʉ 24:12\f* tasa' iya.
\v 7 Kamoro ka'pon amʉ' sa'man annawɨrɨ wakʉ kupʉ pɨ' te'san uya eke pe tʉku'to' kon, tʉnamato' kon mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ eri'nɨto' pen warinpa ena' inke rɨ uko'man nɨto' tʉrʉ iya.
\v 8 E'tane kamoro tiwano' kon pe rɨ te'san mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ i'nairon ana'sipai pʉra te'san mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨri pɨkɨrɨ te'san pɨ', moro isakorotasa' pɨ' ekota'man nɨto' esi mɨrɨ.
\v 9 Moro ewankamanin mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ a'kwarʉ ainʉnpanin e'to' oton tanporon kon ɨri ku'nin nan ka'pon amʉ' pɨ': wapiya Esuwerʉ amʉ' pɨ', mɨrɨ tʉpo Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen;
\v 10 e'tane eke pe iku'to', inamato' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉusewankamai' pʉra e'nɨto' esi tanporo wakʉ ku'nin nan iwano' pe: wapiya Esuwerʉ amʉ' pɨ', mɨrɨ tʉpo Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen pɨ',
\v 11 apʉne pʉra Papa esi pɨ' tenu yawon kenan pe pʉra rɨ.\x - \xo 2:11 \xt Isu'taronomi 10:17\x*
\p 
\v 12 Tanporon kon, main, Mosi' winon piyapai imakoitasa' kon uma'tato' oton mɨrɨ main piyapai rɨ marɨ, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tanporon kon imakoitasa' kon main o'noro eseru utaimenkato' oton main ke.
\v 13 Apʉne pʉra kamoro mɨrɨ main etanin nan esi pen ipokena' pe Papa enu yau, e'tane kamoro main awɨron kon anʉmʉ Papa uya ipokena' ton tukai'.
\v 14 (Kasi pe pʉra, Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen, main, Mosi' winon esanon pen, uya ikupʉ ti'naino kon nɨ main e'to' i'se, main pe rɨ tiwano' kon pe to' esi, main esanon pe pʉra rɨ esii'ma,
\v 15 to' uya enpoika si'kɨrɨ mɨrɨ main e'to' i'se e'menukasa' to' ewan pɨ', to' ewan uya rɨ nɨrɨ ekama to' pɨ', mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ to' usenuminkato' uya rɨ ipoken pʉra to' e'sa' ekama, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉron nɨ a'tai ipoken to' e'sa' ta iya rɨ.)
\v 16 Serɨ e'ku'to' oton Papa uya ama'aino eseru aimenka weyu a'tai Sises Kʉrai poro, wakʉ uyekareei nekamayai'ne' kasa.
\s1 Esuwerʉ Amʉ' Mɨrɨ Awonsi'kɨ Main, Mosi' Winon
\p 
\v 17 Ɨmɨrɨ nin si, Esuwerʉ pe te'sesa'sen; main, Mosi' winon enupɨkɨrɨ te'sen mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Papa pokon pe ɨwe'to' pɨ' tʉutapurɨsen.
\v 18 I'se iye'to' i'tunin pe ɨwesi yau, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ewai' tawon pe te'sen epoi te'sen pɨ' apʉne pʉra main nenupa'pʉ pe ɨwesi pɨ'.
\v 19 Pori' pe ɨwesi yau tenku'na' nan anin pe ɨwesi pɨ', ewarupɨ yau te'san weyu pe ɨwesi pɨ',
\v 20 iya'kwarʉ pʉnon enupanin pe ɨwesi kon pɨ', aiko ton nʉ'kwɨ mʉre amʉ' ti'saai pe ɨwesi pɨ', apʉne pʉra main esi wakʉ pe i'tuto' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ i'nairon yen pe—
\v 21 Ɨmɨrɨ si, tʉron kon enupanin, ɨiwano' pe pe' ɨusenupa pen nɨ? Ɨmɨrɨ ama' pe e'nɨ namai' itekare ekamanin, ama'manin pe' ɨmɨrɨ?
\v 22 Ɨmɨrɨ iyemari'masa' kon ka'pon amʉ' kʉsekumanin tawon, tekumasen pe' ɨmɨrɨ? Ɨmɨrɨ papa tato' ipɨ' pe ika'sa' itewaruma, ɨpʉreman nɨto', use'man nɨto' iwʉ' ton pe' rapumanin ɨmɨrɨ?
\v 23 Ɨmɨrɨ main pɨ' tʉutapurɨsen, main pe' ti'kwɨ'se Papa namanin pe pʉra te'sen ɨmɨrɨ?
\v 24 Iye'menukasa' na'ne' kasa: “Papa ese' e'sapema Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen koro'tau ɨmɨrɨ'nokon uriya',”\f + \fr 2:24 \ft Aisaya 52:5; Isi'kiyerʉ 36:22\f* tawon.
\p 
\v 25 Itepe' e' pe un pi'pɨ puturʉkato' esi main awɨrɨ ɨwesi yau, e'tane main i'kwɨtʉ auya yau, itun pi'pɨ puturʉkasa' pen pe rɨ ɨyena.
\v 26 Kamoro itun pi'pɨ iputurʉkasa' kon pen e'sa' main e'to' i'se awɨrɨ, itun pi'pɨ iputurʉkasa' kon pe pe' to' kupʉ pen?
\v 27 Kʉrɨ ipun pe itun pi'pɨ iputurʉkasa' pen, mɨrɨpan e'tane main awɨron, uya ɨyeno'ma mɨrɨ, ɨmɨrɨ iye'menukasa' main tensen pe esa'\f + \fr 2:27 \fq iye'menukasa' main tensen pe esa'; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq iye'menukasa' tensen pe main winɨ\f* mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ un pi'pɨ puturʉkato' esa', esi main i'kwɨ'nin pe.
\p 
\v 28 Ka'pon esi pen mɨrɨ Esuwerʉ pe kuru kɨpo'po rɨ kʉrɨ rɨ pe iyesi yau, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ kɨpo'po rɨ, ipun pe rɨ un pi'pɨ puturʉkato' esi nɨrɨ pen nɨ.
\v 29 Kane, ka'pon esi mɨrɨ Esuwerʉ pe kuru tʉyau kʉrɨ rɨ pe tesi yau; mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ un pi'pɨ puturʉka esi tepe' ke rɨ ewan wannɨ ma'kʉʉi'tɨ kasa, iya'kwarʉ winɨ, iye'menukasa' main na'ne' awɨron pen nɨ. Pʉse rɨ waraino ka'pon apurɨpɨ'to' esi mɨrɨ ka'pon winɨpaino pen, e'tane Papa winɨpaino pe.\x - \xo 2:29 \xt Isu'taronomi 30:6\x*
\c 3
\s1 Papa Tʉusaurokʉ'pʉ Awɨron
\p 
\v 1 Ɨ'rɨ eponin pe ken si e'nɨ Esuwerʉ pe e'nɨ yau, mɨrɨ pe pʉra ɨ'rɨ epe' pe yun wannɨ pi'pɨ puturʉka?
\v 2 Eke pe rɨ tanporon yau rɨ! Tanporon wapiya, Papa maimu kuru rɨ e'nonka'pʉ mɨrɨ to' ena'.
\p 
\v 3 Ɨ'rɨ pe ken iyesi to' tonpa ton uya apurɨto' pʉra iyesi yau? To' uya apurɨto' pʉra iyesi uya Papa e'to' tʉusauro'sa' awɨrɨ pʉra kupʉ?
\v 4 Pen kuru rɨ! Tɨwɨ Papa nesii i'nai rɨ, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tanporon kon e'tane kasi ye' pe. Iye'menukasa' na'ne':
\q1 “Ipokena' pe ɨusi'tu pa amaimu yau
\q2 ɨyeseru aimenkato' yau itentai ɨyena pa,”\f + \fr 3:4 \ft Eren 51:4\f* tawon.
\p 
\v 5 E'tane ipoken pʉra e'nɨto' uya Papa e'to' ipoken enpoika wakʉ pe kuru, ɨ'rɨ ken si ta? Papa esi wakʉ pe pʉra rɨ uya kota'man nɨto' nepʉ upona'nokon ta? (Ka'pon e'sei'pɨ'to' e' pe rɨ nin si e'kapʉ.)
\v 6 Mɨrɨ kasa iyesi pen! Mɨrɨ kasa iyesi yau, nai kasa Papa non eseru aimenkai'no?
\v 7 Ka'pon nɨ entarumʉ, “Kasi ye' pe esi uya Papa e'to' i'nairon pe koneka yau eke pe iku'to' temo'kai', ɨ'rɨto' pe ken si tʉmakooikenan pe uyeno'ma?”
\v 8 Tapai pʉra pe' nai—kasi ye' pe rɨ ina pɨ' usauro'nɨsa' na'ne' kasa mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉron kon uya ikupʉ, ina uya—“Ɨri ku'pai'nokon wakʉ pe itepe'pʉ e'to' pe,” ta, ta pʉra? To' eno'mato' esi mɨrɨ i'se to' e'to' pe rɨ.
\s1 Ɨnʉ' Ipoken Te'sen Pʉn Nɨ
\p 
\v 9 Ɨ'rɨ ken si? Ina ken pe' si Esuwerʉ amʉ' esi wakʉ\f + \fr 3:9 \fq wakʉ, \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra \fq ɨri\f* ton pe? Parɨ pen nɨ! Ekamaka'sa'nokon nɨ mɨrɨ, Esuwerʉ amʉ' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen esi mɨrɨ ɨsi'kaisa rɨ makoi o'no.
\v 10 Iye'menukasa' na'ne' kasa:
\q1 “Ɨnʉ' rɨ pʉra iyesi ipokena' pe te'sen, tikin nan pʉra rɨ;
\q2 
\v 11 ɨnʉ' rɨ pʉra iyesi ito'ka'nʉ'nin,
\q2 ɨnʉ' rɨ Papa warinpanin.
\q1 
\v 12 Tanporon kon nɨ era'tɨsa' ɨsi'kaisa rɨ siya
\q2 tanporo rɨ to' enasa' se pe rɨ;
\q1 ɨnʉ' rɨ pʉra iyesi wakʉ ku'nin,
\q2 tikin nan pʉra rɨ.”\f + \fr 3:12 \ft Eren 14:1-3; Eren 53:1-3; E'kirisiyastes 7:20\f*
\q1 
\v 13 “To' esen ton esi emenna' ton akasa' uruwai' ton pe;
\q2 to' ani ton esi enku'tɨn nɨto' ku'nin pe.”\f + \fr 3:13 \ft Eren 5:9\f*
\q1 “Ɨkʉi urarii rɨ esi to' e'pi pɨ'.”\f + \fr 3:13 \ft Eren 140:3\f*
\q2 
\v 14 “To' mʉta ton epe'tɨpɨ'sa' e'pa'nʉ'nɨto' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨsipɨ' e'nɨto' ke.”\f + \fr 3:14 \ft Eren 10:7\f*
\q1 
\v 15 “Aitune' pe rɨ to' pʉta ton esi mʉn ennoko pɨ';
\q2 
\v 16 to' utɨ'pʉ e'ma'pʉ tau uma'tan nɨsa' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ usewankaman nɨto' e'nɨmɨ,
\q1 
\v 17 mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉusewankamai' pʉra ka'pon uko'manto' ku'to' to' ni'tunʉ pen.”\f + \fr 3:17 \ft Aisaya 59:8\f*
\q2 
\v 18 “Papa pɨ' to' enari'nʉnto' pʉra rɨ iyesi to' enu yau,”\f + \fr 3:18 \ft Eren 36:1\f*
\m tawon.
\p 
\v 19 Serɨ si i'tu'nokon, tanporo main uya tasa' na'ne', ta iya kamoro main o'no na'ne' nan pɨ', tanporo mʉta e'tʉtʉikato' pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tanporo non pon kon e'to' pe Papa pɨ' ekamanin pe.
\v 20 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', ɨnʉ' rɨ anʉmʉ Papa uya pʉra iyesi ipokena' tukai' main kupʉ iya pɨ'; e'tane ru'ku, main poro makoi i'tunin pe enan.\x - \xo 3:20 \xt Eren 143:2; Kare'siya 2:16\x*
\s1 Ipoken E'nɨ Apurɨto' Poro
\p 
\v 21 E'tane nin si serɨ Papa uya ka'pon amʉ' anʉnto' ipokenan pe usi'tusa', main piyapai, main, Mosi' winon mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Pu'kena' amʉ' nekamayai'ne'.
\v 22 Serɨ ipoken e'nɨto' usi'tusa' uyepʉ Sises Kʉrai apurɨto' poro tanporon kon apurɨnin nan piya'. Tʉponaron pʉra rɨ iyesi,\x - \xo 3:22 \xt Kare'siya 2:16\x*
\v 23 apʉne pʉra tanporon kon nɨ umakoitasa' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ to' u'ma'sa' mɨ airɨ rɨ eke pe Papa ku'to' tepose pʉra,
\v 24 mɨrɨpan kon ekonekasa' tʉuse'mai' pʉra wakʉ nonkasa' iya winɨ e'man nɨto' poro iye'sa' Kʉrai Sises winɨ.
\v 25 Papa uya itʉsa' use'man nɨto' ike pe upɨ'nokon tʉusentu'mato' pe\f + \fr 3:25 \fq use'man nɨto' ike pe upɨ'nokon tʉusentu'mato' pe; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq kʉrɨ tʉkota'man nɨto' i'nɨ'panʉ'nin, makoi mo'kai'ma\f* imʉnʉ apurɨto' poro. Serɨ ku'sa' iya ipokena' pe tesi ekamanin pe, apʉne pʉra a'kʉre'tɨnin pe tesi ke makoi ton pena iye'ku'sa' rʉ'san nonka'pʉ iya tʉponi'simai' pʉra—
\v 26 ikuu'pʉ iya ipoken tesi serɨ a'tai tukai' enpoikanin pe, ipoken teseru esi enpoikanin pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ka'pon amʉ' anʉnnin pe ipokena' pɨkɨron kon pe Sises apurɨto' winɨ.
\p 
\v 27 Nai ken si utapurɨn nɨto'? Mɨrɨ pʉra rɨ iyesi. Ɨ'rɨ iteseru pe? Main pe' awɨrɨ e'nɨ pɨ'? Kane, e'tane apurɨto' pɨ'.
\v 28 Apʉne pʉra ka'pon anʉmʉ Papa uya ipokena' pe ta'nokon apurɨto' winɨ main awɨrɨ e'nɨ winɨ pʉra.
\v 29 Papa pe' esi Esuwerʉ amʉ' rɨken e'to' itese' pɨ' pe? Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen e'to' itese' pɨ' rɨ nɨrɨ pen pe' kʉrɨ? Ewai', Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen nɨ nɨrɨ,
\v 30 tikin nɨ rɨken Papa esi pɨ', ka'pon itun pi'pɨ iputurʉkasa' anʉnton apurɨto' winɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ itun pi'pɨ iputurʉkasa' pen mɨrɨ rɨ marɨ apurɨto' poro.\x - \xo 3:30 \xt Isu'taronomi 6:4; Kare'siya 3:20\x*
\v 31 Apurɨto' pɨ' ken pe' si usauro' nɨ uya main, Mosi' winon pʉra iye'to' pe ikupʉ? Parɨ pen nɨ! E'tane ru'ku, main awɨrɨ e'nɨ'nokon.
\c 4
\s1 Epʉra'an Ekoneka'pʉ Apurɨto' Winɨ
\p 
\v 1 Ɨ'rɨ ken si eporo'pʉ utamokori kon Epʉra'an uya serɨ rupɨ pɨ' ta serɨ?
\v 2 Epʉra'an anʉnsa' pe iyesi yau ipokena' pe inkuu'pʉ winɨ, itapurɨto' ipɨ' esi mɨrɨ—e'tane Papa rau pen.
\v 3 Ɨ'rɨ ta imenukasa' itekare uya? “Epʉra'an uya Papa apurɨ'pʉ, mɨrɨ pɨ' ipokena' pe iyesi,” ta'pʉ ipɨ'.\f + \fr 4:3 \ft Iseneses 15:6; Kare'siya 3:6; v. 22 nɨrɨ\f*
\p 
\v 4 Ka'pon e'tʉrawasoma a'tai, itepe'pʉ esi mɨrɨ irepato' ike tukai' iyesi pen nɨ e'tane iye'tʉrawasomasa' rʉ'pʉ ipɨ' pe iyesi.
\v 5 E'tane rɨ, kʉrɨ ka'pon te'tʉrawasomasen pen pona e'tane Papa apurɨnin ɨri ka'pon anʉnnin ipokena' tukai', apurɨto' iya uya ikupʉ Papa uya anʉnto' pe ipokena' tukai'.
\v 6 Tepi' uya mɨrɨ rɨ marɨ ta isaurokʉ a'tai ka'pon e'to' pɨ' pori' pe Papa uya anʉmʉ a'tai ipokena' pe iyesi tukai', inkupʉnʉ pɨkɨrɨ pen:
\q1 
\v 7 “Pori' pe kamo esi
\q2 ɨri to' nʉkuu'pʉ pɨ' usentu'man nɨsa' kon
\q2 mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ imakooi ton inɨpontɨsa' na'ne' nan.
\q1 
\v 8 Pori' pe kʉrɨ ka'pon esi
\q2 imakooi i'tuto' Itepuru uya pen ipɨ',”\f + \fr 4:8 \ft Eren 32:1-2\f*
\m ta.
\p 
\v 9 Serɨ pori' pe e'nɨto' pe' esi itun pi'pɨ iputurʉkasa' kon iwano' pe rɨken, mɨrɨ pe pʉra itun pi'pɨ iputurʉkasa' kon pen nɨ nɨrɨ katɨ iwano' pe iyesi? Epʉra'an anʉmʉ'pʉ ipokena' tukai' apurɨto' iya pɨkɨrɨ ta pɨ' e'nɨsa'.
\v 10 Ɨ'rɨ waraino ton o'noro serɨ e'kuu'pʉ? Itun pi'pɨ puturʉka'pʉ tʉpo pe' iyesi'pʉ, mɨrɨ pe pʉra irawɨrɨ katɨ? Mɨrɨ tʉpo pen e'tane mɨrɨ rawɨrɨ!
\v 11 Mɨrɨpan uya tʉyun pi'pɨ puturʉkato' eporo'pʉ ento' ipɨ' pe, Papa uya anʉnsa' ipokena' pe enpoikanin pe apurɨto' iya winɨ, itun pi'pɨ puturʉkasa' pe pʉra rɨ marɨ iyesi koro'tau. Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', tanporon kon apurɨnin nan kʉipʉnʉ pe iyesi e'tane itun pi'pɨ iputurʉkasa' kon pen, anʉnsa' kon tato' pe to' pɨ'.\x - \xo 4:11 \xt Iseneses 17:10\x*
\v 12 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ itun pi'pɨ iputurʉkasa' kon kʉipʉnʉ pe rɨ marɨ iyesi, itun pi'pɨ iputurʉkasa' kon pe rɨken to' esi pen e'tane tʉutɨsan nɨ marɨ apurɨto' pʉta'pʉ awɨrɨ ukʉipʉnʉ kon Epʉra'an enau iye'sa' rʉ'pʉ itun pi'pɨ puturʉka rawɨrɨ.
\p 
\v 13 Main poro Epʉra'an mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ imunkɨ amʉ' uya iku'to' pe uya tukai' usauro'nɨsa' eporo'pʉ pen non anʉnto' iya, e'tane anʉn nɨto' tʉuye'sen apurɨto' winɨ.\x - \xo 4:13 \xt Iseneses 17:4-6; 22:17-18; Kare'siya 3:29\x*
\v 14 Apʉne pʉra kamoro tʉuko'mansan main awɨrɨ rɨken esi yau anʉnnin nan pe, apurɨto' esi mɨrɨ itepe' pe pʉra rɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ iku'to' pe uya tukai' usauro'nɨsa' esi mɨrɨ se pe rɨ,\x - \xo 4:14 \xt Kare'siya 3:18\x*
\v 15 apʉne pʉra main uya kota'man nɨto' nepʉ. Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ main pʉra na'ne' airɨ main awɨrɨ pʉra e'nɨto' pʉra iyesi.
\p 
\v 16 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', iku'to' pe uya tukai' usauro'nɨsa' uyepʉ apurɨto' winɨ, iye'ku'to' pe wakʉ nonkasa' winɨ, mɨrɨpan e'kupʉ mɨrɨ a'tai tanporo Epʉra'an munkɨ amʉ' pɨ'—kamoro rɨken main pɨ' te'san pen e'tane kamoro Epʉra'an uya apurɨto' pɨ' te'san nɨ marɨ. Tanporo ukʉipʉnʉ kon pe iyesi.\x - \xo 4:16 \xt Kare'siya 3:7\x*
\v 17 Iye'menukasa' na'ne' kasa: “Ɨkonekasa' uya mɨrɨ tu'kan kon tʉpataron kon kʉipʉnʉ pe,”\f + \fr 4:17 \ft Iseneses 17:5\f* tawon. Epʉra'an esi ukʉipʉnʉ kon pe Papa enu yau, inapurɨnʉ—Papa uko'man nɨto' tʉnin iyeri'sa' ena' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨ'rɨ rɨ esa'nin moro ipʉra rɨ iye'tane moro iyesi kasa.
\p 
\v 18 E'ku'nɨto' ipɨ' pʉra kasa rɨ iye'tane, te'ku'to' yau rɨ Epʉra'an uya apurɨ'pʉ, mɨrɨpan ena'pʉ tu'kan kon tʉpataron kon kʉipʉnʉ pe, ta'pʉ na'ne' tʉpɨ' kasa rɨ, “Mɨrɨ kasa kuru apayan nʉ'san e'to' oton,”\f + \fr 4:18 \ft Iseneses 15:5\f* tawon.
\v 19 Apurɨto' tʉuya yau tɨ'sɨ'mʉnka'nʉ'se pʉra, i'tu'pʉ iya rɨ tʉpun eri'sa' pe rɨ—apʉne pʉra 100 e'to' airɨ rɨ tʉwʉipiyaai esi pɨ'—mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Sera mʉre yen nɨ nɨrɨ esi'pʉ iyeri'sa' pe.\x - \xo 4:19 \xt Iseneses 17:17\x*
\v 20 E'tane rɨ Papa uya ikupʉ tʉuya tukai' tauro'ka'pʉ apurɨ'pʉ iya, apurɨto' iya umeruntɨta'pʉ, mɨrɨpan uya Papa apurɨpɨtʉ'pʉ,
\v 21 ipan pe ti'tui' Papa esi meruntɨ rɨ ikupʉ tʉuya tukai' tʉusaurokʉ'pʉ ku'nin ye'.
\v 22 Mɨrɨ wenai, “Papa uya anʉmʉ'pʉ ipokenan tukai',” tasa' iya.
\v 23 Main, “iku'to' esi'pʉ mɨrɨ,” tawon e'menuka'pʉ kʉrɨ rɨ iwano' pe rɨken pen,
\v 24 e'tane urɨ'nokon nɨ nɨrɨ iwano' pe, anʉnsa' pe ipoken e'nɨto' e'ku'to' oton na'ne'—urɨ'nokon apurɨpɨ' na'ne' nan uyepuru kon Sises i'mʉ'sa'kasa' iya pɨ' eri'nɨto' apai.
\v 25 Itʉrʉ'pʉ eri'nɨto' ya' umakooi kon wenai, mɨrɨpan i'mʉ'sa'ka'pʉ iko'manto' ya' wakʉ pe ekonekan nɨto' pe Papa enu yau.\x - \xo 4:25 \xt Aisaya 53:4-5\x*
\c 5
\s1 Tʉusewankamai' Pʉra Mɨrɨ Awonsi'kɨ Pori' Pe E'nɨ
\p 
\v 1 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', apurɨto' poro Papa uya uyanʉnsa' kon ipokena' pe pɨ', usewankaman nɨto' pʉra iyesi\f + \fr 5:1 \fq usewankaman nɨto' pʉra iyesi; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq tʉusewankamai' pʉra e'nɨto' esa' pe e'nɨpai'nokon\f* Papa pokon pe e'nɨ pɨ' Sises Kʉrai, uyepuru kon poro,
\v 2 iporo epoto' eposa' apurɨto' winɨ serɨ eke nonkasa' iya' iyau e'mʉ'sa'kan nɨsa'nokon na'ne'. Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ epori'ma'nokon\f + \fr 5:2 \fq epori'ma'nokon; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq epori'manpai'nokon; \ft v. 3 yau rɨ nɨrɨ\f* ipokon pe Papa ku'to' eke pe yau e'nɨ'nokon pɨ' e'ku'nɨto' yau.
\v 3 Mɨrɨ kasa rɨken pen, e'tane epori'ma'nokon nɨ nɨrɨ ekota'ma'nokon yau, apʉne pʉra i'tu'nokon ekota'man nɨto' uya sa'man awɨrɨ iku'to' enpa'ka;
\v 4 sa'man awɨrɨ iku'to' uya, eseru wannɨ; mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ eseru wannɨ uya e'ku'nɨto' enpa'ka.
\v 5 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ e'ku'nɨto' uya ika'nɨ' pʉra ku'nɨ pen, apʉne pʉra Papa uya tʉusi'nʉnkato' nonkasa' uyewan kon ya' Wakʉ A'kwarʉ winɨ, itʉsa' iya na'ne' uyena'nokon.
\p 
\v 6 Menyatʉu, iweyu a'tai kuru sa'ne, imeruntɨrʉ pʉra rɨ marɨ e'nɨ'nokon a'tai, Kʉrai\f + \fr 5:6 \fq Kʉrai; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq Me'saya; Papa Nanʉmʉ'pʉ \ft ta e'kwa pe; v. 8 yau nɨrɨ.\f* erikʉ'pʉ Papa uya tasa' pen awɨron kon iwano' pe.
\v 7 Iteseru pen nɨ ɨnʉ' rɨ erikʉ pʉra iyesi ipokena' pe te'sen ka'pon iwano' pe, wakʉ ka'pon iwano' pe ɨnʉ' rɨ e'to' e'tane eri'pai itiwano' pe.
\v 8 E'tane Papa uya ui'nʉnkato' kon tʉuya ya' rɨ enpoika wakʉ pe serɨ yau: Tʉmakooikenan pe rɨ marɨ e'nɨ'nokon koro'tau, Kʉrai erikʉ'pʉ uiwano' kon pe.
\p 
\v 9 Papa uya anʉn nɨsa' ipokena' pe pɨ' imʉnʉ winɨ, mɨrɨ entai rɨ epika'tɨn nɨto' oton kon iporo Papa uya kota'man nɨto' apai!
\v 10 Apʉne pʉra, Papa eyaton pe e'nɨsa'nokon yau, itonpa pe enan nɨsa'nokon Imu eri'to' poro, mɨrɨ entai nin si, itonpa pe enan nɨsa' epika'tɨto' oton iko'manto' poro!
\v 11 Serɨ rɨken nɨ esi pen mɨrɨ kasa, e'tane epori'man nɨ marɨ Papa yau Sises Kʉrai, uyepuru kon poro, iporo Papa tonpa pe enan nɨsa' eposa'nokon na'ne'.
\s1 Uma'tan Nɨto' Atan Poro, Uko'man Nɨto' Kʉrai Poro
\p 
\v 12 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', makoi ewomʉ'pʉ non pona tikin nan ka'pon poro na'ne' kasa kuru, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ uma'tan nɨto' makoi poro, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ serɨ na'ne' kasa uma'tan nɨto' uyee'pʉ tanporon kon ka'pon amʉ' pona. Serɨ ta uya, apʉne pʉra tanporon kon umakoitasa' pɨ'.\x - \xo 5:12 \xt Iseneses 3:6\x*
\v 13 Main, Mosi' winon e'tʉrʉ rawɨrɨ, makoi esi'pʉ non po. E'tane makoi mɨrɨ tato' pʉra iyesi main pʉra na'ne' airɨ.
\v 14 Mɨrɨ nin si e'tane, uma'tan nɨto' e'sa' esa' wannɨ pe Atan si'kɨrɨ Mosi' pʉ'kʉ pona, kamoro rɨ main ti'kwɨ'se, Atan kasa imakoitasa' kon pen nɨ esa' pe, tʉuye'ton ento' ipɨ' pe te'sen.
\p 
\v 15 E'tane repan nɨto' ike esi ɨri ku'sa' Atan uya na'ne' warai pen nɨ. Apʉne pʉra tu'kan kon eri'sa' pe iyesi yau tikin nan ka'pon uya ɨri ku'sa' pɨ', mɨrɨ entai Papa uya wakʉ nonkasa' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ repan nɨto' tikin nan nɨ ka'pon, Sises Kʉrai uya wakʉ nonkasa' winɨ iye'sa', tu'kan kon nɨ ka'pon amʉ' uya eposa' eke pe kuru rɨ!
\v 16 Repan nɨto' ike, kanan, esi pen tikin nan ka'pon, Atan umakoitasa' moron nʉ'pʉ kasa: Eseru aimenkato' esi tikin nan makoi e'ma'pʉka pɨ', mɨrɨpan uya eno'man nɨto' nepʉ; e'tane repan nɨto' uya tu'kan nɨ ɨri ku'pɨ'sa' e'ma'pʉka, mɨrɨpan uya anʉn nɨto' ipokena' pe nepʉ.
\v 17 Apʉne pʉra tikin nan ka'pon uya ɨri ku'sa' winɨ, uma'tan nɨto' e'sa' esa' wannɨ pe yau kʉrɨ rɨ tikin nan ka'pon poro, mɨrɨ entai kuru kamoro eke pe rɨ wakʉ Papa nʉnonka'pʉ eponin nan mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ anʉn nɨto' Papa uya ipokena' pe nʉtʉrʉnʉ esi esa' wannɨ pe uko'man nɨto' yau tikin nan nɨ ka'pon, Sises Kʉrai poro.
\p 
\v 18 Mɨrɨ moron nʉ'pʉ pe, tikin nan ka'pon nʉkuu'pʉ ɨri moron nʉ'pʉ pe tanporon kon ka'pon amʉ' eno'mato' esi'pʉ kasa, mɨrɨ kasa rɨ marɨ tikin nan Papa maimu awɨrɨ e'nɨto' ku'sa' moron nʉ'pʉ esi'pʉ anʉn nɨ Papa uya ipokena' pe uko'man nɨto' ne'nin pe tanporon kon ka'pon amʉ' iwano' pe.
\v 19 Apʉne pʉra tikin nan nɨ ka'pon e'sa' pɨ' main awɨrɨ pʉra iporo tu'kan kon nɨ ena'pʉ tʉmakooikena' nan pe, mɨrɨ kasa rɨ marɨ tikin nan nɨ ka'pon esi pɨ' main awɨron pe tu'kan kon nɨ anʉmʉ Papa uya ipokena' ton pe.
\p 
\v 20 Main e'tonpa'tɨ'pʉ ɨri e'kupʉ epanto' pe. E'tane makoi epansa' yau, wakʉ nonkasa' epansa' miyarɨ rɨ,
\v 21 makoi esi'pʉ na'ne' kasa esa' wannɨ pe uma'tan nɨto' yau, mɨrɨ kasa rɨ marɨ wakʉ nonkasa' e'to' pe esa' wannɨ pe Papa uya anʉn nɨ ipokena' pe poro tɨwɨro' rɨ uko'man nɨto' ne'nin pe Sises Kʉrai, uyepuru kon poro.
\c 6
\s1 Eri'nɨsa' Makoi Ya', Nurɨne E'nɨ Kʉrai Yau
\p 
\v 1 Ɨ'rɨ ken si ta'nokon serɨ, mɨrɨ a'tai? Umakoitan pɨ' rɨ e'nɨ'nokon, wakʉ nonkasa' epanto' pe?
\v 2 Kane ku! Uko'man nɨto' ɨri yau eri'sa'; nai kasa iyau rɨ marɨ uko'man nɨ pɨ' e'nɨ?
\v 3 Mɨrɨ pe pʉra, i'tu auya'nokon pʉra katɨ iyesi urɨ'nokon tanporo iyepa'taisimasa' kon Kʉrai Sises ya' epa'taisima'pʉ ima'tato' ya'?
\v 4 Iye'u'na'tɨsa' pe rɨ e'nɨ'pʉ'nokon; mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', ipokon pe epa'taisiman nɨto' poro uma'tan nɨto' ya', Kʉrai e'mʉ'sa'ka'pʉ terikʉ'pʉ apai kasa kuru eke pe Ikʉipʉnʉ ku'to' poro, urɨ'nokon nɨ nɨrɨ uko'manto' pe iyesi emenna' uko'man nɨto' yau.\x - \xo 6:4 \xt Koro'se 2:12\x*
\p 
\v 5 Ima'tato' yau ipokon pe uta'si'nɨsa' yau, ipokon pe kuru rɨ marɨ uta'si'nɨ'nokon mɨrɨ iye'mʉ'sa'kato' yau.
\v 6 Apʉne pʉra i'tu'nokon pena e'nɨto' eseru pokapɨtʉ'pʉ kurusu' pona ipokon pe makoi pun enato' pe ɨ'sɨ'mʉra,\f + \fr 6:6 \fq ɨ'sɨ'mʉra; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq eno'mato' kon pe\f* makoi poitorʉ ton pe pʉra e'nɨto' kon pe—
\v 7 apʉne pʉra iyeri'sa' pe na'ne' emo'kasa' makoi apai.
\p 
\v 8 Eri'nɨsa' pe iyesi yau Kʉrai pokon pe, apurɨ'nokon ipokon pe rɨ marɨ uko'man nɨ'nokon tukai'.
\v 9 Apʉne pʉra i'tu'nokon pɨ' Kʉrai e'mʉ'sa'kasa' pɨ' eri'nɨsa' apai, iyeri'kapʉ pen kanan; itentai uma'tan nɨto' esi pen.
\v 10 Uma'tan nɨto' iyerikʉ'pʉ na'ne' yau, iyerikʉ'pʉ makoi ya' tikin ite'kwa tʉnakonomaton pe pʉra rɨ; e'tane si iko'manto' nʉko'manʉ'ai'ne', iko'mamʉ Papa iwano' pe i'se iye'to' awɨrɨ.
\p 
\v 11 Mɨrɨ kasa si, ɨsi'tutɨ' ɨri yau ɨuko'manto' kon eri'sa' pe e'tane nurɨne Papa iwano' pe Kʉrai Sises yau.
\v 12 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', makoi kʉse'nin tʉuma'tasen ɨpun kon esa' pe ɨri i'se iye'to' awɨrɨ ɨwesi kon pa.
\v 13 Ɨpun kon pʉ'kʉ rɨ kʉ'tʉtʉu makoi ena', ɨri ku'to' ike pe, e'tane e'tʉtɨ' ru'ku Papa ena', kamoro uma'tan nɨto' apai uko'man nɨto' ya' iyera'tɨsa' kon pe; mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨpun kon pʉ'kʉ itʉtɨ' itena' ipoken e'nɨto' ku'to' ike pe.
\v 14 Apʉne pʉra makoi e'to' pe pʉra iyesi ɨyepuru kon pe, apʉne pʉra main o'no ɨwesi kon pen, e'tane wakʉ nonkasa' o'no.
\s1 Ipoken E'nɨto' Poitorʉ Pe E'nɨ
\p 
\v 15 Mɨrɨ a'tai si, ɨ'rɨ ken? Umakoita'nokon ken pe' si apʉne pʉra main o'no pʉra e'nɨ pɨ' e'tane eke wakʉ nonkasa' o'no e'nɨ pɨ'? Kane ku!
\v 16 I'tu auya'nokon pʉra pe' iyesi ɨye'tʉsa' kon a'tai ka'pon ena' imaimu awɨrɨ ɨwesi kon pa ipoitorʉ ton pe, imaimu awɨrɨ ɨwe'to' kon poitorʉ pe ɨwesi kon? Makoi poitorʉ pe ɨwesi kon yau, uma'tan nɨto' ya' anin, mɨrɨ pe pʉra main awɨrɨ e'nɨto' ya', ipoken uko'man nɨto' ya' anin.
\v 17 E'tane tenki tapai'nokon Papa pɨ', makoi poitorʉ pe rɨ ɨwe'pɨ'sa' kon e'tane, tanporo ɨyewan kon pokon pe ɨyenupato' kon awɨrɨ ɨwe'sa' kon ɨye'tʉsa' kon na'ne' ya'.
\v 18 Makoi apai ɨyemo'kasa' kon; ipoken e'nɨto' Papa enu yau poitorʉ pe ɨyenasa' kon.
\p 
\v 19 Ka'pon pe e'nɨto' yau ekama uya apʉne pʉra ɨ'sɨ'mʉra a'naino kon ɨyeseru kon yau ɨwesi kon pɨ'. Ɨpun kon pʉ'kʉ tʉpɨtʉ'pʉ auya'nokon kasa kuru ɨri poitorʉ pe, eke pe rɨ tepansen ɨri ena', mɨrɨ kasa si itʉtɨ' ipoken Papa enu yau poitorʉ pe e'nɨto' ya', wakʉ pe ɨwesi kon pa.
\v 20 Makoi poitorʉ pe ɨwesi kon a'tai, ipoken te'sen Papa enu yau ku'to' auya'nokon pʉra rɨ iyesi'pʉ.
\v 21 Ɨ'rɨ ken si wakʉ mepota'tʉi mɨrɨ a'tai serɨ pe ipɨ' si mɨpiyɨ'atʉi'ne' apai? Mɨrɨ ton moron nʉ'pʉ esi uma'tan nɨto'!
\v 22 E'tane nin si, ɨyemo'kasa' kon pɨ' makoi apai mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Papa poitorʉ pe nin si ɨyenasa' kon, wakʉ si ɨneporonʉ kon esi ayanin kon wakʉ pe e'nɨto' ya', mɨrɨpan moron nʉ'pʉ esi inke rɨ uko'man nɨto'.
\v 23 Apʉne pʉra makoi epe'pʉ esi uma'tan nɨto', e'tane Papa e'repato' ike esi inke uko'man nɨto' Kʉrai Sises, uyepuru kon poro.\f + \fr 6:23 \fq poro, \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra \fq yau\f*
\c 7
\s1 Ento' Ipɨ' Emari'man Nɨto' Apai
\p 
\v 1 I'tu auya'nokon pʉra pe' nai, utonpa ton—ka'pon amʉ' main, Mosi' winon i'tunin nan auro'ka uya serɨ—meruntɨ pe ka'pon pɨ' main esi iko'mamʉ pʉ'kʉ pona rɨken?
\v 2 Ento' ipɨ' pe, iyemari'masa' uri'san utauronsa' mɨrɨ tʉtaan'pʉ pona nurɨne iyesi koro'tau, e'tane itaan'pʉ eri'sa' yau, iyemo'kasa' nin si mɨrɨ emari'man nɨto' ku'nin main apai.
\v 3 Mɨrɨ a'tai nin si, tʉron nɨ warawo' ya' iyemari'masa' yau nurɨne rɨ tʉtaan'pʉ esi koro'tau, tekumasen temari'masa' e'tane ta mɨrɨ ipɨ'. E'tane itaan'pʉ eri'sa' pe iyesi yau, iyemo'kasa' mɨrɨ main apai, mɨrɨpan esi tekumasen temari'masa' e'tane tato' ipɨ' pe pʉra, tʉron nɨ warawo' mari'ma tane iya rɨ.
\p 
\v 4 Mɨrɨ kasa si, utonpa ton, ɨmɨrɨ'nokon nɨ nɨrɨ main yau ɨuko'manto' kon apai ɨyeri'sa' kon Kʉrai pun poro, tʉron nɨ iwano' pe ɨwesi kon pa, kʉrɨ iye'mʉ'sa'kasa' rʉ'pʉ terikʉ'pʉ apai, Papa iwano' pe epetan nɨto' pe.
\v 5 Apʉne pʉra u'naino kon umakooi kon\f + \fr 7:5 \fq umakooi kon; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq ipun; \ft v. 25 yau rɨ nɨrɨ\f* esi a'tai uyesa' kon pe, ɨri ɨnku'pai e'nɨto' upakasa' main winɨ esi'pʉ e'tʉrawasoman pɨ' upun kon yau, mɨrɨ si epetan nɨ'pʉ uma'tan nɨto' iwano' pe.
\v 6 E'tane serɨ pe nin si, uyauron nin nʉ'pʉ kon ya' eri'nɨ winɨ, emo'kan nɨsa' main apai emenna' Iya'kwarʉ eseru yau iyapiyo' pe e'nɨto' kon pe, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ penaro' iye'menukasa' main awɨron pen nɨ.
\s1 Makoi Ya' E'suran Man
\p 
\v 7 Ɨ'rɨ ken si ta'nokon serɨ, mɨrɨ a'tai? Makoi pe pe' main esi? Ta pen nɨ! I'nai rɨ, makoi mɨrɨ tukai' si'tui'no pen nɨ, e'tane main poro nin i'tusa' uya. Apʉne pʉra si'tui'no pen nɨ tonpa iwano' i'se e'nɨto' ipan pe, main uya, “Ɨtonpa iwano' i'se kesii ipan pe,”\f + \fr 7:7 \ft E'sotas 20:17; Isu'taronomi 5:21\f* tasa' pʉra iyesi yau.
\v 8 E'tane makoi, iku'to' uya iwinɨ ta'sii' apiyontɨn nɨto' winɨ, uya uyau tanporon nɨ i'se ipan pe esi ku'sa'. Apʉne pʉra main pʉra iyesi a'tai, makoi esi iyeri'sa' pe.
\v 9 Pena nurɨne iye'sa' rʉ'pʉ urɨ main pʉra iyesi a'tai; e'tane apiyontɨn nɨto' uye'sa' a'tai, makoi usenpoika'pʉ,
\v 10 mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ erikʉ'pʉ si. I'tu'pʉ uya mɨrɨ rɨ si mɨrɨ main uko'man nɨto' ne'nin pe iku'sa' uya rɨ uma'tan nɨto' kuru rɨ nee'pʉ.
\p 
\v 11 Makoi uya apiyontɨn nɨto' apurɨsa' mɨrɨpan uya uyenku'tɨsa' uya uwɨsa' mɨrɨ main poro.\x - \xo 7:11 \xt Iseneses 3:13\x*
\v 12 Mɨrɨ pɨ', main esi wakʉ pe, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ apiyontɨn nɨto' esi wakʉ pe, ipokena' pe, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ wakʉ pe.
\v 13 Mɨrɨ ken pe' si wakʉ pe te'sen ena'pʉ mɨrɨ upona uma'tan nɨto' pe? Kane ku! E'tane makoi e'to'ka'nʉ'to' pe makoi pe, uma'tan nɨto' ku'sa' iya uyau wakʉ pe te'sen poro rɨ, main uya apiyontɨn nɨto' poro makoi enato' pe ti'tusen pe ɨri pe kuru rɨ.
\p 
\v 14 I'tu'nokon main esi Papa A'kwarʉ winon pe; e'tane urɨ esi Iya'kwarʉ pɨkɨron pe pʉra, ikʉrʉpo'pomasa' pe makoi poitorʉ pe.
\v 15 Unkupʉnʉ i'tu uya pʉra rɨ iyesi, apʉne pʉra ɨnku'pai e'to' kupʉ uya pʉra iyesi, e'tane uyewaruma kupʉ uya.\x - \xo 7:15 \xt Kare'siya 5:17\x*
\v 16 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ, ɨnku'pai pʉra e'to' kupʉ uya yau, wakʉ pe main esi ta uya rɨ.
\v 17 Iyesi na'ne' kasa, urɨ pe iyesi pen nʉku'ai'ne', e'tane makoi uyau nʉko'manyai'ne'.
\v 18 I'tu uya wakʉ uko'mamʉ pʉra iyesi uyau, mɨrɨ na'ne' u'naino ipan makoi yau.\f + \fr 7:18 \fq makoi yau; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq upun yau\f* Apʉne pʉra wakʉ pe na'ne' ɨnku'pai esi, e'tane arɨ uya pʉra iyesi.
\v 19 Apʉne pʉra siku'ai'ne' esi wakʉ ɨnku'pai e'to' pe pʉra; ɨri, ɨnku'pai pʉra e'to' kupʉ uya—serɨ kupʉ pɨ' rɨ uko'mamʉ.
\v 20 Serɨ si ɨnku'pai e'to' pen kupʉ uya yau, urɨ uya ikupʉ pen, e'tane makoi uyau nʉko'manyai'ne' uya ikupʉ.
\p 
\v 21 Mɨrɨ kasa si, serɨ main e'tʉrawasoma pe i'tusa' uya: Wakʉ ɨnku'pai esi a'tai, ɨri esi mɨrɨ moro upiyau.
\v 22 Uyau Papa iwano' main pɨ' tepori'masen urɨ;
\v 23 e'tane tʉron nɨ main e'tʉrawasoma ene uya upun pʉ'kʉ ton yau, usenuminkato' iwano' main pokon pe usewa'noma kupʉ iya, mɨrɨpan uya ukoneka main iwano' makoi na'si'pʉ pe, te'tʉrawasomasen upun pʉ'kʉ ton yau.
\v 24 Pokoi rɨ sa'ne urɨ! Ɨnʉ' uya upika'tɨ serɨ uma'tan nɨto' meruntɨrʉ apai uyau e'tʉrawasoman pɨ' na'ne'?
\v 25 Tenki ta Papa pɨ'—Sises Kʉrai, uyepuru kon poro!
\p Mɨrɨ pɨ' si, urɨ rɨ usenuminkato' yau esi Papa iwano' main poitorʉ pe, e'tane u'naino makoi yau makoi iwano' main poitorʉ pe esi.
\c 8
\s1 Uko'man Nɨto' Iya'kwarʉ Poro
\p 
\v 1 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', kamoro Kʉrai Sises yau na'ne' nan eno'mato' pʉra iyesi serɨ pe,\f + \fr 8:1 \ft Tʉron nɨ ton emen imenukasa' ton uya iponantɨpɨ'sa', \fq tʉuko'mansan i'naino makoi awɨrɨ pʉra e'tane a'kwarʉ awɨrɨ,\f*
\v 2 apʉne pʉra Kʉrai Sises poro uko'man nɨto' A'kwarʉ iwano' main uya umo'kasa'\f + \fr 8:2 \fq umo'kasa'; \ft tʉron nɨ imenukasa' ton yau, \fq ɨmo'kasa' kon; \ft tʉron nɨ rɨ marɨ yau, \fq umo'kasa' kon\f* makoi mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ uma'tan nɨto' iwano' main apai.
\v 3 Apʉne pʉra main, Mosi' winon esi'pʉ na'ne' ɨ'sɨ'mʉra ikupʉ iya pʉra, i'naino makoi\f + \fr 8:3 \fq i'naino makoi; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq ipun; \ft v. 4-5, 8-9, 12 yau rɨ nɨrɨ\f* uya a'tu'mʉnka'nʉ'sa' ke, Papa uya ikuu'pʉ tiwano' tʉmu tenno'se tʉmakooikenan ka'pon kasa makoi mo'kanin pe tʉtʉsen pe.\f + \fr 8:3 \fq makoi mo'kanin pe tʉtʉsen pe; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq makoi iwano' pe\f* Mɨrɨpan uya makoi eno'ma'pʉ tʉmakooikenan ka'pon yau,\f + \fr 8:3 \fq tʉmakooikenan ka'pon yau; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq ipun yau\f*
\v 4 ipokena' pe e'nɨ i'se main e'to' e'seposa' e'to' pe eke pe uyau'nokon, u'naino kon umakooi kon pɨkɨrɨ tʉuko'mansan pe pen e'tane urɨ'nokon Iya'kwarʉ pɨkɨrɨ tʉuko'mansan.
\p 
\v 5 Kamoro tʉuko'mansan ti'naino kon tʉmakooi kon awɨrɨ uya tʉusenuminkato' kon tʉsa' mɨrɨ ti'naino kon e'to' i'se pona; e'tane kamoro tʉuko'mansan Iya'kwarʉ awɨrɨ uya tʉusenuminkato' kon tʉsa' mɨrɨ Iya'kwarʉ e'to' i'se pona.
\v 6 Tʉmakooikenan ka'pon usenuminkato'\f + \fr 8:6 \fq Tʉmakooikenan ka'pon usenuminkato'; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq Usenuminkan nɨto' e'tʉsa' pun pɨ'\f* esi uma'tan nɨto', e'tane Iya'kwarʉ e'to' itesa' pe te'sen usenuminkato' esi uko'man nɨto' pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ usewankaman nɨto' pen;
\v 7 apʉne pʉra tʉmakooikenan usenuminkan nɨto'\f + \fr 8:7 \fq tʉmakooikenan usenuminkan nɨto'; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq usenuminkan nɨto' e'tʉsa' pun pɨ'\f* esi ɨsɨ pe Papa pɨ'. Papa iwano' main ya' iye'tʉrʉ pʉra iyesi, mɨrɨ kupʉ iya poken pʉra rɨ nɨrɨ iyesi.
\v 8 Kamoro to' i'naino makoi e'to' itesanon pe uya Papa pori'ma poken pʉra rɨ iyesi.
\p 
\v 9 E'tane rɨ, ɨmɨrɨ'nokon a'naino kon amakooi kon esi pen ɨyesa' kon pe, e'tane Iya'kwarʉ, Papa A'kwarʉ uko'mamʉ yau ayau'nokon. Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨnʉ' rɨ esi yau Kʉrai A'kwarʉ esa' pe pʉra, Kʉrai iwano' pe pʉra rɨ iyesi.
\v 10 E'tane ayau'nokon Kʉrai esi yau, ɨpun kon esi iyeri'sa' pe apʉne pʉra makoi esi pɨ', e'tane aya'kwarʉ kon esi nurɨne apʉne pʉra Papa uya ayanʉmʉ kon pɨ' ipokena' ton pe.
\v 11 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Sises i'mʉ'sa'kanin nʉ'pʉ iyerikʉ'pʉ apai A'kwarʉ uko'mamʉ yau ayau'nokon, kʉrɨ rɨ Kʉrai i'mʉ'sa'kanin nʉ'pʉ iyerikʉ'pʉ apai uya rɨ marɨ tʉuma'tasen ɨpun kon repa mɨrɨ iko'manto' ke Ta'kwarʉ poro, ayau'nokon nʉko'manyai'ne'.\x - \xo 8:11 \xt 1 Koren 3:16\x*
\p 
\v 12 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', utonpa ton, unkupʉnʉ kon kuru esi—e'tane u'naino kon umakooi kon pɨ' pen, tʉuko'mansan pe iteseru awɨrɨ pen.
\v 13 Apʉne pʉra ɨuko'mamʉ kon pe iyesi yau a'naino kon amakooi kon awɨrɨ, ɨyerikʉ kon; e'tane Iya'kwarʉ winɨ ipun nʉkupʉ'pʉ ipoken pʉra tʉsa' auya a'tai ima'tato' ya', ɨuko'mamʉ kon nɨ,
\v 14 apʉne pʉra kamoro, Papa A'kwarʉ narɨnʉ ton esi Papa munkɨ pe pɨ'.
\v 15 Apʉne pʉra iya'kwarʉ eposa' auya'nokon pʉra iyesi enari'ke' pe e'nɨ poitorʉ pe kanan ɨwesi kon pa pen, e'tane Iya'kwarʉ eposa' auya'nokon imunkɨ pe ɨkonekanin kon,\f + \fr 8:15 \fq imunkɨ pe ɨkonekanin kon; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq tʉmunkɨ pe ɨmo'kanin kon\f* mɨrɨpan winɨ, “Apa,\f + \fr 8:15 \fq Apa; \ft Arami' maimu, \fq Papai \ft ta e'kwa pe.\f* Papai,” ta'nokon.\x - \xo 8:15 \xt Ma' 14:36; Kare'siya 4:6\x*
\v 16 Iya'kwarʉ uya ekama tiwano' pe uya'kwarʉ kon pokon pe, urɨ'nokon esi Papa munkɨ pe tukai'.
\v 17 Serɨ si munkɨ pe e'nɨ'nokon yau, intʉrʉnʉ anʉnnin pe e'nɨ—Papa nʉtʉrʉnʉ anʉnnin pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Kʉrai nanʉmʉnʉ intʉrʉnʉ anʉnnin pe iya'kɨrɨ, i'nai rɨ iyekota'mato' yau e'nɨsa' yau, eke pe iku'to' yau rɨ marɨ e'nɨto' pe.\x - \xo 8:17 \xt Kare'siya 4:5-7\x*
\s1 Serɨ Enta' Eke Pe E'nɨto'
\p 
\v 18 Usenuminka serɨ pe ekota'man na'ne' esi urɨ'nokon yau tʉusenpoika ton Papa uya ikupʉ winɨ eke pe iku'to' kaisa rɨ i'nʉnke' pe iyesi pen nɨ.
\v 19 Ika'sa' kon enurikʉ tenu ke esii'ma Papa munkɨ amʉ' usenpoika enupɨkɨrɨ.
\v 20 Tanporo ika'sa' ton ko'manʉkʉ'pʉ itiwano' pe ika'sa' epoto' iya piyapai, ɨko'manpai iyesi pɨ' pen. Serɨ e'kuu'pʉ iye'moronkato' pe ku'nin nʉ'pʉ poro, te'ku'se
\v 21 ika'sa' kon nɨ emo'kato' pe ma'tanʉ'nin meruntɨrʉ apai, iyemo'kasa' kon Papa munkɨ pe eke pe te'ton kon pe.
\p 
\v 22 I'tu'nokon tanporo ika'sa' kon a'nʉmʉ mʉre entunʉkʉ pɨ' e'nɨ kasa serɨ pʉ'kʉ pona rɨ.
\v 23 Mɨrɨ kasa rɨken pen, e'tane urɨ'nokon nɨ nɨrɨ, iyepiya'tɨ pe te'sen Wakʉ A'kwarʉ eponin nʉ'san nɨ a'nʉmʉ u'nau'nokon enurikʉ tenu ke esii'ma uyanʉnto' kon pɨ' imunkɨ pe, upun kon e'mato'.\x - \xo 8:23 \xt 2 Koren 5:2-4\x*
\v 24 Apʉne pʉra serɨ e'ku'nɨto' yau epika'tɨn nɨsa'. E'tane e'ku'nɨto' tensen pe na'ne' esi e'ku'nɨto' pe pʉra kuru rɨ. Ɨnʉ' ken te'ku'sen tenawon pɨ' rɨ?
\v 25 E'tane e'ku'nɨ pe iyesi yau uyenau'nokon pʉra na'ne' pɨ', itenupɨkɨrɨ e'nɨ mɨrɨ tʉuseta'kai' pʉra.
\p 
\v 26 Mɨrɨ kasa rɨ, Iya'kwarʉ uya upika'tɨ kon ɨ'sɨ'mʉra e'nɨto' yau. Ɨpʉreman nɨto' i'tu'nokon pʉra iyesi, e'tane Iya'kwarʉ rɨ ɨpʉrema upona'nokon ta'nʉnse main uya ekama poken pʉra rɨ.
\v 27 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ kʉrɨ uyewan kon warinpanin uya Iya'kwarʉ usenuminkato' i'tu, apʉne pʉra Iya'kwarʉ ɨpʉrema wakʉ ton Papa nʉkupʉ'san pona Papa e'to' i'se awɨrɨ.
\s1 Entakanin Nan Entai Rɨ
\p 
\v 28 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ i'tu'nokon tanporon yau rɨ Papa e'tʉrawasoma wakʉ pe ti'nʉnkanin ku'nin pe,\f + \fr 8:28 \ft Tʉron nɨ imenukasa' ton yau, \fq i'tu'nokon tanporon nɨ e'tʉrawasoma a'samʉtʉ yau wakʉ ku'nin pe kamoro Papa i'nʉnkanin nan pɨ'\f* ikɨ'masa' kon mɨrɨto' pe ta'pʉ tʉuya awɨrɨ.\f + \fr 8:28 \fq e'tʉrawasoma wakʉ pe ti'nʉnkanin ku'nin pe, ɨkɨ'masa' kon mɨrɨto' pe ta'pʉ tʉuya awɨrɨ; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq e'tʉrawasoma a'samʉtʉ yau kamoro i'nʉnkanin nan pokon pe wakʉ pe te'sen ne'nin pe—kamoro ikɨ'masa' kon pokon pe mɨrɨto' pe ta'pʉ iya awɨrɨ.\f*
\v 29 Kamoro iwano' pe Papa uya wapiya i'tu'pʉ pena kanan to' koneka'pʉ iya Tʉmu kasa to' e'to' pe iwaraino kon pe, eke kuru iye'ka'sa' kon entaino pe wapiyaro' tʉmu pe tu'kan kon tonpa ton koro'tau.
\v 30 Kamoro si pena tʉnkoneka'san, to' kɨ'masa' iya rɨ marɨ; kamoro tʉnkɨ'ma'san, anʉmʉ iya ipokena' pe; kamoro tʉnanʉmʉ'san ipokena' pe, kupʉ iya eke pe rɨ marɨ.
\p 
\v 31 Ɨ'rɨ ken si ta serɨ ei'nin pe? Papa esi pe iyesi yau uwenai'nokon pe, ɨnʉ' ken si esi uyewa'nomanin kon pe?
\v 32 Kʉrɨ rɨ Tʉmu teme'nin nʉ'pʉ pen, e'tane inonkanin nʉ'pʉ tanporon kon urɨ'nokon iwano' pe—nai kasa ken urɨ'nokon repa iya pʉra nesii'no ipokon pe wakʉ pe rɨ tanporon ke rɨ?
\v 33 Ɨnʉ' uya nɨrɨ ken Papa nanʉmʉ'san pɨ' ɨri ton ta? Papa kʉrɨ rɨ anʉnnin ipokena' pe.
\v 34 Ɨnʉ' kʉrɨ eno'manin? Kʉrai Sises, iyeri'sa' rʉ'pʉ—mɨrɨ entai, iye'mʉ'sa'kasa' rʉ'pʉ uko'man nɨto' ya'—esi na'ne' Papa emiyatʉ enwo'netʉ winɨ, urɨ'nokon pona rɨ nɨrɨ ɨpʉreman pɨ' te'sen.
\v 35 Ɨnʉ' uya pantakan Kʉrai uya ui'nʉnkato' kon apai? Ɨ'rɨ uya katɨ, usewankaman nɨto' uya, sa'man yau e'nɨto' uya, mɨrɨ pe pʉra iwenai pʉra kota'man nɨto' uya mɨrɨ pe pʉra iwankan uya, mɨrɨ pe pʉra ipon pʉra e'nɨto' uya, mɨrɨ pe pʉra ɨsɨ yau e'nɨto' uya, mɨrɨ pe pʉra supara uya katɨ?
\v 36 Iye'menukasa' na'ne' kasa:
\q1 “Ɨmɨrɨ'nokon epika'tɨto' pe uma'tan nɨto' yau ina esi pata tʉko'manʉ'se;
\q2 karimeru amʉ' iwɨto' kon pe iku'sa' kon kasa rɨ ina esi,”\f + \fr 8:36 \ft Eren 44:22\f*
\m tawon.
\m 
\v 37 Kane, tanporo serɨ ton yau'ne e'nɨ'nokon entakanin nan entai kuru rɨ, kʉrɨ ui'nʉnkanin kon poro.
\v 38 Apʉne pʉra apurɨsa' uya uma'tan nɨto' mɨrɨ pe pʉra uko'man nɨto', inserʉ amʉ' rɨ mɨrɨ pe pʉra makoi amʉ' rɨ,\f + \fr 8:38 \fq makoi amʉ' rɨ; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq ka' epuru ton\f* serɨ pe na'ne' mɨrɨ pe pʉra serɨ enta' na'ne', mɨrɨ pe pʉra ɨ'rɨ rɨ meruntɨ rɨ,
\v 39 ka'tawon nɨ mɨrɨ pe pʉra i'nawon nɨ, mɨrɨ pe pʉra ɨ'rɨ rɨ tanporo ika'sa' yawon, uya pantakan pʉra rɨ iyesi Papa uya i'nʉnkan nɨto' apai Kʉrai Sises, uyepuru kon yau na'ne'.
\c 9
\s1 Eke Pe Kuru Tesi Pɨ' Papa Uya Anʉn Nɨto'
\p 
\v 1 I'nairon pe usaurokʉ Kʉrai yau—kasi pe esi pen, uya'kwarʉ uya apɨtanʉkʉ Wakʉ A'kwarʉ yau—
\v 2 eke pe kuru ipan pe upokoitato' man mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ iyereuta pʉra uyewan yau upokoitato' esi.
\v 3 Ipa'nʉ'sa' pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ imo'kasa' pe Kʉrai piyapai esi i'se e'ai', utonpa ton pika'tɨnin pe, kamoro kuru tʉponaron kon upokon pe,
\v 4 ka'pon amʉ' Esuwerʉ pon kon. To' iwano' pe munkɨ wannɨ pe to' anʉnsa' esi; to' iwano' pe rɨ Papa a'kwarii esi, to' iwano' pe rɨ ekonekan nɨto' esi, to' iwano' pe rɨ main eporo esi, to' iwano' pe ɨpʉreman nɨto', use'man nɨto' iwʉ' tau Papa apurɨpɨ'to' esi mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ikupʉ uya tasa' rʉ'san esi, to' iwano' pe.\x - \xo 9:4 \xt E'sotas 4:22\x*
\v 5 To' iwano' pe rʉko' amʉ' tɨpiya ton esi, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Kʉrai ka'pon pe te'to' winɨ u'tɨsa' to' apai, Papa, tanporon nɨ epoino, tɨwɨrɨ rɨ apurɨpɨtʉ nesii!\f + \fr 9:5 \fq Kʉrai ka'pon pe te'to' winɨ u'tɨsa' to' apai, Papa, tanporon nɨ epoino, tɨwɨrɨ rɨ apurɨpɨtʉ nesii! \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq Kʉrai, tanporon nɨ entaino. Papa apurɨpɨtʉ nesii tɨwɨrɨ rɨ! \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq Kʉrai, Papa tanporon entaino rɨ apurɨpɨtʉ nesii tɨwɨrɨ rɨ!\f* Amen.
\p 
\v 6 Papa Maimu ɨpʉreme'sa' kasa iyesi pen. Apʉne pʉra tanporon kon Esuwerʉ apai iu'tɨsa' kon esi pen Esuwerʉ pe.
\v 7 Ipayan nʉ'san pe rɨ to' esi pɨ' tanporo Epʉra'an munkɨ pe to' esi pen. E'tane mɨrɨ kasa pʉra kuru rɨ; “Aisi' poro ɨmunkɨ amʉ' e'seporo mɨrɨ,”\f + \fr 9:7 \ft Iseneses 21:12\f* tasa'.
\v 8 Tʉron nɨ pe tato' yau, ka'pon i'naino kon\f + \fr 9:8 \fq ka'pon i'naino kon\ft —Epʉra'an payan Esimerʉ, Ekarʉ mʉre poron kon pɨ', ta serɨ uya. (Apʉne Kare'siya Pon kon 4:22-23 enkɨ.)\f* esi pen Papa munkɨ pe, e'tane ikupʉ uya tukai' usauro'nɨsa' munkɨ ton esi Epʉra'an munkɨ pe.
\v 9 Apʉne pʉra se kasa ikupʉ uya tawon usekama'pʉ: “Iweyu pe iku'sa' rʉ'pʉ a'tai\f + \fr 9:9 \fq Iweyu pe iku'sa' rʉ'pʉ a'tai; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq Serɨ a'tai ne'sepoyai'ne' wʉipiya yau\f* enna'po, mɨrɨ a'tai Sera e'to' oton tʉmʉre ke,”\f + \fr 9:9 \ft Iseneses 18:10, 14\f* tukai'.
\p 
\v 10 Mɨrɨ rɨken pe pʉra, e'tane Rupe'ka munkɨ amʉ' esi'pʉ tikin nɨ ikʉipʉnʉ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ kʉrɨ rɨ rɨ to' kʉipʉnʉ pe urɨ'nokon tamokorii, Aisi'.
\v 11 Mɨrɨ rɨ e'tane, munui' amʉ' entu rawɨrɨ mɨrɨ pe pʉra ɨ'rɨ rɨ wakʉ mɨrɨ pe pʉra ɨri kupʉ to' uya rawɨrɨ—moro Papa uya anʉnto' mɨrɨto' pe tukai' e'to' esi'pʉ:
\v 12 tʉrawaso winɨ pen e'tane kʉrɨ ikɨ'manin winɨ—ta'pʉ ipɨ', “Irui e'to' oton takon apiyo' pe,”\f + \fr 9:12 \ft Iseneses 25:23\f* ta'pʉ.
\v 13 Iye'menukasa' na'ne' kasa: “Seko' i'nʉnkasa' uya, e'tane I'sa ewaruma'tɨsa' uya,”\f + \fr 9:13 \ft Mara'kai 1:2-3\f* tukai'.
\p 
\v 14 Ɨ'rɨ ken si ta mɨrɨ a'tai? Ɨri pe pe' Papa esi ta? Pen kuru rɨ!
\v 15 Apʉne pʉra Mosi' pɨ' ta iya,
\q1 “Ɨsentu'mapai rɨ e'to' ipɨ' pɨ' usentu'ma,
\q2 aiko kapai rɨ e'to' ipɨ' pɨ' aiko ta uya,”\f + \fr 9:15 \ft E'sotas 33:19\f*
\m tasa' iya.
\v 16 Mɨrɨ pɨ' si ka'pon e'to' i'se pɨ' mɨrɨ pe pʉra inkuu'pʉ pɨ' iyesi pen, e'tane Papa usentu'mato' pɨ' iyesi.
\v 17 Apʉne pʉra iye'menukasa' itekare uya ta, Peero pɨ': “Ɨi'mʉ'sa'kasa' uya serɨto' pe, umeruntɨrʉ enpoikato' pe uya ayau mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ uyese' usekamato' pe tanporo non yau,”\f + \fr 9:17 \ft E'sotas 9:16 (LXX)\f* ta iya.
\v 18 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', Papa esi tʉusentu'masen ɨsentu'mapai te'to' ipɨ' pɨ' rɨ, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ansa'mantanʉ'pai te'to' rɨ sa'mantanʉkʉ iya.
\p 
\v 19 Ɨtonpa kon uya ta upɨ': “Ɨ'rɨ pe ken si iyesi pɨ' Papa uya upona'nokon eno'ma? Ɨnʉ' uya iteseru wa'kʉtʉ?” ta.
\v 20 Aiko sɨ, ka'pon. Ɨnʉ' ɨmɨrɨ Papa Maimu ei'pɨtʉ pa? “Inkaa'pʉ uya pe' ta mɨrɨ tʉka'nin nʉ'pʉ pɨ', ‘Ɨ'rɨto' pe uka'sa' auya se kasa?’”\f + \fr 9:20 \ft Aisaya 29:16; 45:9\f* ta?
\v 21 Ɨinɨ ka'nin pe' e'to' pe pʉra tʉmeruntɨrʉ yau iyesi mɨrɨ rɨ ɨinɨ pun ke eke pata weyu a'tai tapurɨsen mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉweyu ke pʉra rɨ tapurɨsen ka'nin pe?
\p 
\v 22 Ɨ'rɨ pe iyesi Papa uya anʉnsa' pe iyesi yau kota'man nɨto' enpoikato' pe tʉuya mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉmeruntɨrʉ usi'tuto' pe, uya imoronka tʉuseta'kai' pʉra kota'man nɨto' ton ipɨ'—iyekonekasa' kon tʉuma'tato' kon pe?
\v 23 Ɨ'rɨ pe iyesi serɨ ku'sa' iya yau eke pe tʉku'to' ipɨ' usi'tuto' pe tʉusentu'mato' ton ipɨ', inkoneka'san pena eke pe to' e'to' pe—
\v 24 urɨ'nokon nɨ, inkɨ'ma'san nɨ marɨ, Esuwerʉ amʉ' apai rɨken pen, e'tane Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen piyapai rɨ marɨ?
\v 25 Oseya yau ta pɨ' na'ne' kasa:
\q1 “‘Umunkɨ,’ ta uya to' pɨ' umunkɨ amʉ' pen nɨ pɨ';
\q2 mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ‘Ui'nʉn,’ ta uya ipɨ' ui'nʉn pen nɨ pɨ',”\f + \fr 9:25 \ft Oseya 2:23\f*
\m ta,
\v 26 mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ,
\q1 “Iye'ku'to' oton to' pɨ',
\q2 ‘Umunkɨ amʉ' pen nɨ ɨmɨrɨ'nokon,’ ta'pʉ yau kuru rɨ,
\q1 ‘Papa, tʉuko'mansen munkɨ amʉ',’ tato' oton to' pɨ',”\f + \fr 9:26 \ft Oseya 1:10\f*
\m tasa' iya.
\p 
\v 27 Aisaya uya Esuwerʉ ekare'tɨ ukɨ'pɨ'nʉmʉ:
\q1 “Esuwerʉ amʉ' tu'kanoro e'tane rɨ parau e'pi pon wɨ'sɨ' kasa rɨ,
\q2 tu'ke pʉra to' tonpa'san epika'tɨto' oton.
\q1 
\v 28 Apʉne pʉra Itepuru uya
\q2 iyekota'mato' ya' non tʉrʉ inke pʉra mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨ'rɨ kupʉ poken pʉra,”\f + \fr 9:28 \ft Aisaya 10:22-23\f*
\m ta.
\p 
\v 29 Aisaya uya wapiya ekamasa' na'ne' kasa:
\q1 “Itepuru meruntɨ pe kuru te'sen ye' uya rɨken
\q2 upayan kon pʉra unonkasa' kon yau,
\q1 Satan kasa ena'nokon nesii'no,
\q2 mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Komora kasa e'nɨ'nokon nesii'no,”\f + \fr 9:29 \ft Aisaya 1:9\f*
\m tukai'.
\s1 Esuwerʉ Amʉ' Apurɨnin Nan Pen
\p 
\v 30 Ɨ'rɨ ken si ta mɨrɨ a'tai? Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen, ipoken e'nɨto' ku'nin nʉ'san pen, uya si eposa', tanʉnto' kon ipokena' pe apurɨto' winɨ teposen;
\v 31 e'tane Esuwerʉ amʉ', main ipoken e'nɨto' ku'nin nʉ'san, uya eposa' pʉra iyesi.
\v 32 Ɨ'rɨ pe iyesi pɨ'? Apʉne pʉra to' uya ikuu'pʉ apurɨto' iyawɨrɨ pʉra, tʉrawaso winɨ iyesi tato' pe rɨ. To' e'pi'po'pʉ “e'pi'pon nɨto' tɨ'” pona.
\v 33 Iye'menukasa' na'ne' kasa:
\q1 “Entɨ', inonkasa' uya Sayan po, tɨ', ka'pon amʉ' e'pi'poto' ipona
\q2 mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ, tɨ', to' eno'manin,
\q1 mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ kʉrɨ, kʉrɨ rɨ si apurɨnin pe te'sen ɨpiyɨ'to' oton pen,”\f + \fr 9:33 \ft Aisaya 8:14; 28:16\f*
\m tukai'.
\c 10
\p 
\v 1 Utonpa ton, uyewan e'to' i'se mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨpʉremato' Papa pɨ' esi Esuwerʉ amʉ' epika'tɨto' pe.
\v 2 To' pɨ' rɨ usaurokʉ Papa i'tuto' tʉuya'nokon pɨ' kuru rɨ ipan pe to' e'tʉsa' tukai', e'tane to' e'to' ipan pe e'tʉpai esi Papa i'tuto' pɨ' pen nɨ.
\v 3 To' uya Papa uya anʉn nɨto' ipoken e'nɨto' ya' ku'sa' se pe rɨ pɨ', mɨrɨpan kon e'warinpasa' tiwano' kon nɨ nin ipoken e'nɨto' ɨnkonekapai, to' e'tʉsa' pʉra iyesi Papa uya anʉn nɨto' ipoken e'nɨto' pe ya'.
\v 4 Kʉrai esi main, Mosi' winon u'ma'sa' pe rɨ,\f + \fr 10:4 \fq Kʉrai esi main, Mosi' winon u'ma'sa' pe rɨ; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq Kʉrai esi main, Mosi' winon a'ku'tɨsa' pe rɨ\f* tanporon kon nɨ apurɨnin nan iwano' pe Papa uya anʉn nɨ ipokena' pe e'nɨto' ya'.
\p 
\v 5 Mosi' uya ekama se na'ne' kasa ipoken e'nɨto' esi main winɨ: “Ka'pon serɨ ton ku'nin uko'mamʉ mɨrɨ ton winɨ,”\f + \fr 10:5 \ft Ripaiti'kas 18:5\f* ta.
\v 6 E'tane Papa nanʉmʉnʉ ipokena' pe e'nɨto' ya' apurɨto' winɨ te'sen uya ta: “Kʉkai ɨyewan yau, ‘Ɨnʉ' enuku Epʉn pona?’\f + \fr 10:6 \ft Isu'taronomi 30:13\f*” kʉkai ta (Kʉrai nu'tɨnin pe ta e'kwa pe),
\v 7 “mɨrɨ pe pʉra, ‘Ɨnʉ' u'tɨ serɨ i'nawon ya'?’\f + \fr 10:7 \ft Isu'taronomi 30:13\f*” kʉkai ta (Kʉrai arʉ'nʉ'nin pe eri'nɨsa' apai ta e'kwa pe).
\v 8 E'tane ɨ'rɨ ken si ta Mosi' uya? “Main esi a'ko pe ɨpiyau; anta nau iyesi mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨyewan yau,”\f + \fr 10:8 \ft Isu'taronomi 30:14\f* ta iya, apurɨto' maimu si ina nekamayai'ne':
\v 9 Anta ke ekama auya yau, “Sises esi Epuru wannɨ,” tukai', mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ apurɨi'ma ɨyewan yau Papa uya i'mʉ'sa'ka'pʉ iyeri'sa' apai, ɨyepika'tɨ rɨ.
\v 10 Apʉne pʉra ɨyewan pokon pe apurɨ auya mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨyekoneka, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ anta ke ekama auya mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ si ɨyepika'tɨ.
\v 11 Imenukasa' itekare nɨkayai'ne' kasa, “Kʉrɨ apurɨ pɨ' na'ne' ɨpiyɨ'to' pʉra rɨ iyesi,”\f + \fr 10:11 \ft Aisaya 28:16\f* nɨkayai'ne'.
\v 12 Apʉne pʉra Esuwerʉ amʉ' esi tʉron nɨ pe Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen kasa pʉra tato' pʉra rɨ iyesi—kʉrɨ rɨ rɨ epuru esi tanporon kon epuru pe, mɨrɨpan uya eke pe rɨ wakʉ tʉrʉ tanporon kon tesa'nin nan pona,
\v 13 apʉne pʉra, “Tanporon kon Itepuru ese' esa'nin nan epika'tɨto' oton,”\f + \fr 10:13 \ft Isowerʉ 2:32\f* tasa' iya.
\p 
\v 14 Nai kasa ken tʉnapurɨnʉ kon pen nɨ esakʉi'no to'? Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ, nai kasa ken ɨ'rɨ rɨ tʉneta'pʉ kon ipɨ' pen nɨ apurɨi'no to'? Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ, nai kasa ken to' uya eta, ɨnʉ' uya rɨ itekare ekama tane pʉra rɨ to' pɨ'?
\v 15 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ, nai kasa ken itekare ekama to' uya tenno'sa' kon pen nɨ e'tane? Iye'menukasa' na'ne' kasa, “Ɨ'rɨ pan wakʉ ton nɨ i'ta ton kamoro wakʉ itekare ne'nin nan!”\f + \fr 10:15 \ft Aisaya 52:7\f* tawon.
\p 
\v 16 E'tane tanporo Esuwerʉ amʉ' esi'pʉ pen wakʉ itekare awɨrɨ. Aisaya uya tasa' kasa, “Epuru, ɨnʉ' uya ina nekamanʉ itekare apurɨsa'?”\f + \fr 10:16 \ft Aisaya 53:1\f* tawon.
\v 17 Itepe'pʉ pe, apurɨto' uyepʉ tekamasen eta winɨ, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tekamasen useta Kʉrai maimu poro ina nekamanʉ pe te'sen.
\v 18 E'tane ekama'po uya: To' uya pe' eta pʉra iyesi'pʉ? A'tai kanan ma:
\q1 “To' maimu utɨsa' siya rɨ non awɨrɨ,
\q2 to' maimu utɨsa' non u'matʉ ya' rɨ,”\f + \fr 10:18 \ft Eren 19:4\f*
\m tasa'.
\v 19 Ekama'pokapʉ uya kanan: Esuwerʉ uya pe' ito'ka'nʉkʉ pʉra iyesi'pʉ? Wapiya rɨ, Mosi' uya ta,
\q1 “Ɨyɨkɨntanʉkʉ uya 'nokon mɨrɨ kamoro tʉpataron kon pen nɨ winɨ;
\q2 asakoropa uya 'nokon mɨrɨ ito'ka'nʉ'nin nan pen nɨ tʉpataron kon winɨ,”\f + \fr 10:19 \ft Isu'taronomi 32:21\f*
\m ta.
\v 20 Mɨrɨ a'tai nin si Aisaya uya ta mɨrɨ enari'mʉra esii'ma,
\q1 “Kamoro uwarinpanin nan pen nɨ uya uyeporo'pʉ;
\q2 kamoro nai yau nai tawon nan pen nɨ ena' usenpoika'pʉ,”\f + \fr 10:20 \ft Aisaya 65:1\f*
\m ta.
\v 21 E'tane Esuwerʉ pɨ' ta iya,
\q1 “Pata tʉko'manʉ'se rɨ uyemiyatʉ tɨnkai' uko'mamʉ
\q2 ka'pon amʉ' main awɨron kon pen mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ sa'man nɨ itewan ton ena',”\f + \fr 10:21 \ft Aisaya 65:2\f*
\m ta iya.
\c 11
\s1 Esuwerʉ Pʉ'kʉ Rʉ'san Apurɨton Kon
\p 
\v 1 Ɨyekama'po uya ken si: Papa uya pe' tʉmunkɨ amʉ' ewaruma'tɨsa'? Kane ku! Urɨ rɨ nɨrɨ Esuwerʉ pon, Epʉra'an pa rʉ'pʉ, Pensiman ko' winɨpaino.\x - \xo 11:1 \xt Piri'pai 3:5\x*
\v 2 Papa uya tʉmunkɨ ton ewaruma'tɨsa' pʉra iyesi, iwapiya rɨ tʉni'tu'san. I'tu auya pʉra pe' nai iye'menukasa' itekare uya ta Iraisa pɨ' ipʉ'kʉ yau—Esuwerʉ amʉ' pataka'pʉ iya Papa pɨ' ɨri pe to' e'sa' pɨ':
\v 3 “Itepuru, amaimu ekamanin nan pu'kena' amʉ' wɨpɨtʉ'pʉ to' uya, mɨrɨpan kon uya ɨyena' use'man nɨto' apon a'morʉpɨtʉ'pʉ; urɨ rɨken e'nonkasa', mɨrɨpan kon esi urɨ rɨ nɨrɨ ɨnwɨka'pai,”\f + \fr 11:3 \ft 1 Kin Amʉ' 19:10, 14\f* tawon?
\v 4 Ɨ'rɨ ken si tukai' Papa uya eikʉ'pʉ nai? “Uiwano' pe 7,000 kaisaron kon nonkasa' uya man iye'sekunkasa' kon pen Peyarʉ pɨ',”\f + \fr 11:4 \ft 1 Kin Amʉ' 19:18\f* tukai'.
\v 5 Mɨrɨ kasa rɨ marɨ, serɨ a'tai tu'ke pʉra to' tonpa'san esi wakʉ nonkasa' winɨ anʉnsa' kon.
\v 6 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ wakʉ nonkasa' winɨ iyesi yau, tʉrawaso winɨ iyesi pen; mɨrɨ kasa iye'sa' yau, wakʉ nonkasa' esi pen nɨ mɨrɨ wakʉ nonkasa' pe.\f + \fr 11:6 \ft Tʉron nɨ imenukasa' ton uya \fq wakʉ nonkasa' pe. E'tane tʉrawaso ton winon pe iyesi yau, wakʉ inonkasa' pe pʉra rɨ nin si iyesi mɨrɨ; mɨrɨ pe iyesi yau, tʉrawaso esi mɨrɨ tʉrawaso pe pʉra rɨ, \ft ta.\f*
\p 
\v 7 Ɨ'rɨ ken? Ipan pe tʉnwarinpa'pʉ kon eposa' Esuwerʉ amʉ' uya pʉra iyesi, e'tane tʉron kon to' tonpa ton anʉnsa' kon uya rɨken eporo'pʉ. Tʉron kon to' tonpa ton ewan usa'manta'pʉ,
\v 8 iye'menukasa' na'ne' kasa:
\q1 “Papa uya to' repa'pʉ epe' rɨ e'nɨto' a'kwarʉ ke,
\q2 en ton to' uya ene namai'
\q2 mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ pana ton to' uya eta namai',
\q1 serɨ wʉi pʉ'kʉ pona rɨ,”\f + \fr 11:8 \ft Isu'taronomi 29:4; Aisaya 29:10\f*
\m tukai'.
\v 9 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Tepi' uya ta:
\q1 “Tɨwɨ to' tepʉrʉʉi nesii mare pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ to' sa'manin pe,
\q2 to' e'pi'poto' ipona pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ to' kota'manin pe.
\q1 
\v 10 Tɨwɨ to' enu newarumamʉi to' uya ene namai',
\q2 mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ to' a'poi nʉse'mei tɨwɨro' pe rɨ,”\f + \fr 11:10 \ft Eren 69:22-23\f*
\m ta.
\s1 Are'na'tɨsa' Ipanta Ton
\p 
\v 11 Ekama'pokapʉ uya kanan: To' rɨ pe' e'pi'po'pʉ tʉuta'mo'kai' te'mʉ'sa'ka ton kon pe pʉra? Pen nɨ! E'tane ru'ku, apʉne pʉra main pʉremekʉ to' uya pɨ', epika'tɨn nɨto' uye'sa' Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen piya', Esuwerʉ amʉ' ɨkɨntanʉ'nin pe.
\v 12 E'tane main pʉreme'sa' to' uya uya eke pe pata pʉremato' ne'sa' yau, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ to' eno'masa' uya Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen pʉremato' eke pe kupʉ yau, mɨrɨ entai kuru si eke pe rɨ pʉreman nɨto' nepʉ tanporo wakʉ pe to' konekasa' Papa uya, uya!
\p 
\v 13 Ɨmɨrɨ'nokon auro'ka uya, Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen. Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen ena' itekare ekamai' enno'sa' pe esi wenai, eke pe kuru utʉrawasooi kupʉ uya,
\v 14 te'ku'se utonpa ton ɨkɨntanʉ'nin pe, to' tonpa ton nɨ epika'tɨto' pe.
\v 15 To' uya ewaruma'tɨto' esi yau non konekanin pe, ɨ'rɨ pe to' uya anʉnto' uya ikupʉ? Iyeri'sa' kon na'po kasa iyesi nurɨne to' e'to' ya'.
\v 16 Ipʉ'kʉ pe wapiyaro' iteperu ki'masa' tʉsa' enasa' yau wakʉ pe, mɨrɨ a'tai nin si tanporon itonpa esi mɨrɨ wakʉ pe; imi' ton esi wakʉ pe, mɨrɨ kasa kanan ipanta ton esi mɨrɨ.
\p 
\v 17 Ipanta tonpa ton anpɨ'pʉ pe iyesi yau, ɨmɨrɨ si, mɨ airon are' enpu pe ɨwe'tane, ike ipata'pʉ yai rɨ are'na'tɨsa', mɨrɨpan nin si usewekʉ ite'ku are' mi' winon pɨ',
\v 18 mɨrɨ ton ipanta ton pɨ' katapurɨi. Ikupʉ auya yau, se pɨ' ɨsenuminka': Imi' esa' pe ɨwesi pen, e'tane imi' esi ɨyesa' pe.
\v 19 Mɨrɨ a'tai si, ta auya, “Ipanta ton anpɨ'pʉ urɨ ke itare'na'tɨto' pe.”
\v 20 Iye'to' pe rɨ iyesi, e'tane anpɨ'pʉ mɨrɨ apʉne pʉra apurɨ pʉra iyesi pɨ', mɨrɨpan ɨmɨrɨ nin si esi mɨrɨ apurɨto' auya winɨ ɨye'mʉ'sa'kasa'. Mɨ pe ke'kupʉi, e'tane enari'nʉnkɨ.
\v 21 Apʉne pʉra Papa uya i'naino ipanta ton enkurunpasa' pʉra iyesi yau, ɨmɨrɨ rɨ nɨrɨ enkurunpa iya pʉra iyesi mɨrɨ.
\p 
\v 22 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', mannʉ' pe Papa e'to' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨsɨ yai konekan nɨto' iya pɨ' ɨsenuminka': ɨsɨ yai kamoro ita'mo'kasa' ton konekato' iya, e'tane mannʉ' pe ɨpɨ' iyesi, mannʉ' pe iye'to' yau ɨwesi yau kanan. Mɨrɨ pʉra ɨwesi yau, ɨmɨrɨ rɨ nɨrɨ a'tɨ mɨrɨ.
\v 23 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tapurɨi' pʉra e'nɨto' yau to' esi pʉra iyesi yau, to' rɨ are'na'tɨ ipona, apʉne pʉra Papa rɨ esi to' are'na'tɨka'nin pe rɨ kanan.
\v 24 Mɨrɨ rɨ ta tane, auta'tɨsa' pe iyesi yau are' e' apai mɨ airon nɨ i'naino airon, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ i'naino waraino pen nɨ utare'na'tɨsa' ipatamasa' are' e' ya', mɨrɨ entai kuru rɨ nin serɨ ton, i'naino ton ipanta ton, esi mɨrɨ itare'na'tɨ tʉye' are' e' kuru rɨ nin pona!
\s1 Tanporo Esuwerʉ Amʉ' Epika'tɨto' Oton
\p 
\v 25 Tonan tawon i'tunin nan pe pʉra ɨwesi kon i'se pʉra e'ai', utonpa ton, autaperʉka kon namai': Esuwerʉ uya sa'man pe enan i'tusa' mɨrɨ ipʉ'kʉ pe rɨ tanporo Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen ewomʉ pʉ'kʉ pona.
\v 26 Mɨrɨ kasa nin si tanporo Esuwerʉ amʉ' epika'tɨ mɨrɨ, iye'menukasa' na'ne' kasa:
\q1 “Mo'kanin uye'to' oton Sayan winɨ;
\q2 Papa pʉra e'nɨto' ra'tɨ iya Seko' piyapai.
\q1 
\v 27 Serɨ nin si mɨrɨ\f + \fr 11:27 \fq Serɨ nin si mɨrɨ; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq Serɨ e'to' oton\f* to' pokon pe ekonekato' iwinɨ
\q2 to' makooi mo'kasa' uya a'tai,”\f + \fr 11:27 \ft Aisaya 59:20-21; 27:9; Iseremaya 31:33-34\f*
\m tukai'.
\p 
\v 28 Wakʉ itekare esi na'ne' awɨrɨ, ɨ'seyaton pe to' esi mɨrɨ ɨmɨrɨ'nokon pɨkɨrɨ; e'tane utanʉn nɨto' esi na'ne' awɨrɨ, to' usi'nʉnka tʉtamokori kon pɨkɨrɨ,
\v 29 apʉne pʉra Papa nʉtʉrʉnʉ ton mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ kɨ'man nɨto' iya esi inna'ponʉ pe pʉra.
\v 30 Pena Papa Maimu awɨrɨ pʉra me'ta'tʉine' kasa, main awɨrɨ pʉra to' esi moron nʉ'pʉ pe ɨpɨ'nokon usentu'man nɨto' eposa' auya'nokon,
\v 31 mɨrɨ kasa rɨ marɨ, Papa usentu'masa' ɨpɨ'nokon moron nʉ'pʉ pe, to' nin si enasa' main awɨrɨ pʉra tʉpɨ'nokon usentu'man nɨto' epoto' pe tʉuya'nokon.
\v 32 Apʉne pʉra Papa uya tanporo ka'pon amʉ' a'sisa' main awɨrɨ pʉra e'nɨto' ya', tanporo to' pɨ' tʉusentu'mato' pe.
\s1 Papa Apurɨpɨ'to'
\q1 
\v 33 Eke si i'nawon nɨ Papa e'to' eke pe ipu'ketʉ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ i'tunin pe iye'to'!\f + \fr 11:33 \fq Papa e'to' eke pe ipu'ketʉ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ i'tunin pe iye'to'; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq Papa e'to' eke pe, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ipu'ketʉ pe, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ i'tunin pe iye'to'!\f*
\q2 Iwarinpa pokena' pen nɨ eseru aimenkato' iya,
\q2 mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ e'ma'pʉka pokena' pen nɨ ite'ma'pʉ!
\q1 
\v 34 “Ɨnʉ' uya Itepuru usenuminkato' i'tu'pʉ?
\q2 Mɨrɨ pe pʉra, ɨnʉ' rɨ esi'pʉ ipana'tɨnin pe?”\f + \fr 11:34 \ft Aisaya 40:13\f*
\q1 
\v 35 “Ɨnʉ' uya rɨ Papa repa'pʉ,
\q2 Papa uya te'mato' pe?”\f + \fr 11:35 \ft Isopu 41:11\f*
\q1 
\v 36 Apʉne pʉra iwinɨpai mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ iporo mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ itiwano' pe tanporon nɨ esi.
\q2 Itiwano' pe eke pe iku'to' nesii, tɨwɨrɨ rɨ! Amen.\x - \xo 11:36 \xt 1 Koren 8:6\x*
\c 12
\s1 Nurɨnan Use'man Nɨto' Ike
\p 
\v 1 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', ɨyekama'po uya 'nokon kuru, utonpa ton, ɨsentu'ke' pe Papa esi pɨ', te'tʉsen pe ɨwesi kon pa nurɨnan use'man nɨto' ton ike ye' pe, wakʉ, Papa pori'manin ye' pe—iya'kwarʉ\f + \fr 12:1 \fq iya'kwarʉ, \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra \fq ikupʉ poken\f* yau apurɨpɨ'to' auya'nokon.
\v 2 Serɨ orʉ eseru awɨrɨ inke ke'tʉu, e'tane ɨsensimatɨ' kuru ɨusenuminkato' kon eseru kupʉ winɨ emenna' pe, Papa eseru wakʉ pe te'sen i'tunin pe nin si ɨwesi kon pa mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ wakʉ pe iyesi ta kon pa—pori'manin pe te'sen mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ima'takʉʉi pʉra te'sen.
\p 
\v 3 Apʉne pʉra wakʉ nonkasa' uyena' winɨ ta uya tanporo ɨmɨrɨ'nokon pɨ': Eke pe kuru rɨ ɨpɨ'nokon ke'ku'tʉu ɨwe'to' kon entai rɨ, e'tane ru'ku, eseru aimenkato' yai ɨsentɨ' nurɨnan yai, apurɨto' auya'nokon ke ti'tui' Papa uya ɨrepasa' kon na'ne' ike.
\v 4 Tikin nɨ upun kon esa' esi na'ne' kasa tu'ke rɨ ipʉ'kʉ ton e'tane, mɨrɨpan serɨ ton ipʉ'kʉ ton esi pen tikin nɨ itʉrawasooi,
\v 5 mɨrɨ kasa Kʉrai yau urɨ'nokon, tu'kan kon nɨ ena tikin nɨ ipun pe, mɨrɨpan esi ɨsipʉ'kʉ pe'ne.\x - \xo 12:5 \xt 1 Koren 12:12\x*
\v 6 Ɨsi'tai repapɨ'nɨto' esi, wakʉ nonkasa' uyena'nokon awɨrɨ. Ka'pon repato' ike pe pu'kena' pe usauro'nɨto' esi yau, tɨwɨ napurɨi apurɨto' tʉuya yau iyesi kaisarɨ rɨ.
\v 7 Apiyo' pe iyesi yau, tɨwɨ apiyo' pe nesii; enupanin pe iyesi yau, tɨwɨ enupan pɨ' nesii;
\v 8 pori'mapɨ'nin pe iyesi yau, tɨwɨ pori'man pɨ' nesii; entu'manin nan repanin pe iyesi yau, tɨwɨ amʉre'mʉra ne'repai; epuru pe iyesi yau, tɨwɨ esa' wannɨ pe nesii ari'kena' pe; tʉusentu'masen pe iyesi yau, tɨwɨ pori' pe esii'ma nʉkupʉi.\x - \xo 12:8 \xt 1 Koren 12:4-11\x*
\s1 Usi'nʉnkan Nɨto'
\p 
\v 9 Usi'nʉnkan nɨto' nesii i'nairon pe kuru. Ɨri eseru ewaruma'tɨtɨ'; wakʉ pɨ' ata'sitɨ'.
\v 10 Tʉusi'nʉnkasen pe e'tɨ' ɨsitonpa pe. Ɨtonpa kon tʉnamai' ɨyentaino kon pe e'tɨ'.
\v 11 Emiya'ne' pe ke'tʉu, e'tane ɨnku'paino ye' pe kuru aya'kwarʉ kon ke, Itepuru apiyo' ton pe e'tɨ'.
\v 12 Pori' pe e'ku'nɨto' yau, ɨsɨ yau e'nɨ moronkanin pe e'tɨ', ɨpʉreman yau te'nonkasen pe pʉra.
\v 13 Papa munkɨ amʉ' tekota'masan tʉrepai' e'tɨ'. Ka'kʉran ereutanʉ'sa' a're'tɨto' eseru tʉku'se e'tɨ'.
\p 
\v 14 Tʉwɨpʉremai' wakʉ kupʉ auya'nokon wenai ɨkota'manin kon pona e'tɨ', te'pa'nʉ'se pʉra e'tɨ'.\x - \xo 12:14 \xt Ma'siu 5:44; Ʉru' 6:28\x*
\v 15 Tepori'mai' tepori'masan pokon pe e'tɨ'. Tʉukaranse tʉukaransan pokon pe e'tɨ'.
\v 16 Wakʉ pe ɨseseru yau tʉko'mansan pe e'tɨ'. Mɨ pe te'ku'san pe pʉra e'tɨ', e'tane se pe te'san pokon pe te'san pe e'tɨ'.\f + \fr 12:16 \fq se pe te'san pokon pe te'san pe; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq se pe rʉ'kwɨ rɨ te'san tʉrawasooi ye' ɨnku'paino pe e'tɨ'\f* Tʉutaperʉkasan pe pʉra e'tɨ'.\x - \xo 12:16 \xt Ipu'ketʉ 3:7\x*
\p 
\v 17 Ɨri ku'nin nʉ'pʉ ɨpɨ'nokon kʉse'matʉu ɨri ke. Ti'tui' wakʉ iku'tɨ' ka'pon amʉ' uya ɨyentane'nokon.
\v 18 Ikupʉ poken iyesi yau, ɨiwano' kon pe ɨwe'to' kon awɨrɨ, ɨko'mantɨ' ɨsɨ pe pʉra tanporon kon pokon pe.
\v 19 Kɨse'matʉu, utonpa ton, e'tane Papa uya kota'man nɨto' pata tʉku'se e'tɨ', apʉne pʉra iye'menukasa' esi: “Urɨ iwano' mɨrɨ e'man; urɨ uya rɨ e'ma,” ta Itepuru uya.\f + \fr 12:19 \ft Isu'taronomi 32:35\f*
\v 20 Mɨrɨ pe pʉra:
\q1 “Iwan pe ɨyeyaton esi yau, a're'tɨkɨ;
\q2 tuna'kiri' ke iyesi yau, iwo'pakɨ.
\q1 Serɨ kupʉ auya uya enkena' kamarʉka' amʉranʉkʉ mɨrɨ i'pai pona,”\f + \fr 12:20 \ft Ipu'ketʉ 25:21-22\f*
\m tasa' iya.
\v 21 Ɨri kuru kʉsenanin ɨyentai'nokon, e'tane ɨri entai enatɨ' wakʉ ke.
\c 13
\s1 Eke Ton Ena' E'tʉn Nɨto'
\p 
\v 1 Tanporon kon e'tʉto' pe iyesi eke ton esa' wannɨ pe te'san ena', apʉne pʉra moro ɨnʉ' rɨ eke pʉra iyesi Papa nʉ'mʉ'sa'ka'pʉ pen. Eke pe na'ne' nan esi Papa nʉ'mʉ'sa'ka'san pe.
\v 2 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', ɨnʉ' rɨ eke pe te'sen ewa'nomanin uya Papa nʉkuu'pʉ ewa'noma mɨrɨ, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ kamoro mɨrɨ ku'nin nan uya eseru aimenkato' nepʉ mɨrɨ tʉpona'nokon nɨ.
\v 3 Apʉne pʉra nari' pe te'san pen ton nɨ kamoro esanon wannɨ ipokena' ku'nin nan pona, e'tane kamoro nin ipokena' pen ku'nin nan. Eke pɨ' pe' enari'mʉra e'pai me'atʉu? Ipokena' ken si iku'tɨ' ayapurɨpɨ'to' kon pe iya nin si.
\v 4 Apʉne pʉra Papa poitorʉ pe iyesi wakʉ pe ɨku'nin kon pe. E'tane ipokena' pen ku'sa' auya'nokon yau, ipɨ' enari'nʉntɨ', notʉn pe supara esa' pe te'sen pen kʉrɨ rɨ. Papa poitorʉ kʉrɨ rɨ, Papa uya kota'man nɨto' ne'nin kamoro ɨri ku'nin nan kota'mai'.
\v 5 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', e'tʉn nɨto' pe kuru iyesi eke ton ena', to' uya kota'man pɨ' rɨken pen, e'tane ewan wannɨ uya i'tu pɨ' rɨ.
\v 6 Mɨrɨ wenai rɨ nɨrɨ tamʉranʉ'sen pʉrata e'ma auya'nokon mɨrɨ, apʉne pʉra Papa poitorʉ pe eke ton esi pɨ', inke rɨ esa' wannɨ pe te'san pe.
\v 7 Tanporo ɨnwoma'san kon e'matɨ': Tamʉranʉ'sen omasa' auya'nokon yau, e'ma'tɨ'; ɨntʉrʉnʉ kon yau ɨye'womasa' kon yau, e'matɨ'; eke pe iku'to' yau ɨye'womasa' kon yau, eke pe iku'ka'tɨ' rɨ; inamato' yau ɨye'womasa' kon yau, inamaka'tɨ' rɨ.\x - \xo 13:7 \xt Ma'siu 22:21; Ma' 12:17; Ʉru' 20:25\x*
\s1 Ɨsi'nʉnkatɨ', Apʉne Pʉra A'ko Pe Iweyu Esi Pɨ'
\p 
\v 8 Ɨ'rɨ rɨ te'masen kʉsenkurunpatʉu te'mai' pʉra, ɨusi'nʉnkato' kon nɨken enkurunpatɨ' miyarɨ rɨ usi'nʉnkan pɨ', apʉne pʉra kʉrɨ tʉtonpa i'nʉnkanin uya main a'ku'tɨsa' pe iyesi.
\v 9 Apiyontɨn nɨto' ike ton, “Iyemari'masa' pe esii'ma kekumai,” “Ɨnʉ' rɨ kʉ'wɨnɨi,” “Ama' pe kesii,” “Ipan pe ɨtonpa iwano' i'se kesii,”\f + \fr 13:9 \ft E'sotas 20:13-15; Isu'taronomi 5:17-19, 21\f* mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨ'rɨ ton nɨ apiyontɨn nɨto' esi na'ne' amʉrasa' mɨrɨ se tikin nan iporo e'nɨto' yau: “Ɨtonpa i'nʉnkakɨ, mɨsi'nʉnkayai'ne' kasa rɨ,”\f + \fr 13:9 \ft Ripaiti'kas 19:18\f* tawon.
\v 10 Usi'nʉnkan nɨto' esi ɨsɨ pe tʉtonpa ku'nin pen nɨ. Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', usi'nʉnkan nɨto' esi main awɨrɨ e'nɨ ekamanin pe.
\p 
\v 11 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ serɨ si iku'tɨ', serɨ pe e'nɨto' to'ka'nʉkʉ pe. Iweyu e'seposa' man aupakato' kon ɨye'nʉnto' kon apai, apʉne pʉra a'ko pe si epika'tɨn nɨto' esi pɨ' wapiya apurɨ a'tai iyesi'pʉ entai.
\v 12 Ewarupɨ utɨiwaka'nɨ pɨ' man; pata ema'kapʉ pe rɨ iyesi. Mɨrɨ pɨ' ewarupɨ yau tʉku'sen amaka'pai'nokon mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ a'kwa amataai ya' enai'ma.
\v 13 Wakʉ pe te'san pe e'nɨpai'nokon, wʉi naino kon pe, ipɨ' rɨ te'kamai' e'taripan pɨ' pʉra mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ te'taripasan pe pʉra, ekuman pʉra mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ipan pe ɨri kupʉ pɨ' ɨko'manpai e'nɨ pɨ' pʉra, ɨseseru yau pʉra e'nɨto' pʉra mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨkɨntan pʉra.
\v 14 E'tane ru'ku, Itepuru Sises Kʉrai ke epontɨnpai'nokon, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ a'naino kon makoi\f + \fr 13:14 \fq a'naino kon makoi, \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra \fq ɨpun kon\f* e'to' i'se pɨ' tʉusenuminkai' pʉra imaimu awɨrɨ ɨwe'to' kon pɨ'.
\c 14
\s1 Ɨ'sɨ'mʉn Mɨrɨ Awonsi'kɨ Pana'pan
\p 
\v 1 Ɨ'sɨ'mʉra na'ne' apurɨto' iya yau, anʉntɨ', iteseru taimenkai' pʉra tʉron nɨ pe iteseru esi pɨ' ipokon pe te'sei'pɨ'se pʉra.
\v 2 Tikin nan ka'pon uya apurɨto' uya ikupʉ tanporon pɨ' rɨ tenta'nasen pe, e'tane tʉron nɨ, ɨ'sɨ'mʉra te'sen apurɨto' iya enta'na ipatamasa' kiyari pɨ' rɨken.
\v 3 Ka'pon tanporon pɨ' rɨ tenta'nasen, kʉrɨ ipatamasa' kiyari pɨ' tenta'nasen pɨ' kʉ'sewaruma'tɨnin, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ka'pon tanporon pɨ' tenta'nasen pen kʉrɨ tanporon pɨ' tenta'nasen pe te'sen eno'manin, apʉne pʉra Papa uya anʉnsa' pe iyesi pɨ'.
\v 4 Ɨnʉ' pe ken ɨwesi, ka'pon poitorʉ rɨ eseru aimenka pa? Itesa' pona iye'mʉ'sa'kasa' pe iyesi mɨrɨ pe pʉra ita'mo'kasa' pe rɨ. Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ iye'mʉ'sa'ka rɨ si, apʉne pʉra Itepuru uya iye'mʉ'sa'kato' pe ikupʉ pɨ'.
\p 
\v 5 Tʉron nɨ ka'pon pona eke tʉnamasen pe tikin nan wʉi esi tʉron nɨ ton kasa pʉra; tʉron nɨ ka'pon pona tanporon nɨ wʉi esi ɨsi'kaisa rɨ. Tʉkaisarɨ'nokon tʉusenuminkato' kon awɨrɨ to' nesii i'se te'to' kon pe kuru.
\v 6 Kʉrɨ eke pe kuru tikin nan wʉi esi nɨkayai'ne' uya ikupʉ mɨrɨ Itepuru iwano' pe. Kʉrɨ o' anyai'ne' uya anɨ mɨrɨ Itepuru iwano' pe, apʉne pʉra Papa pɨ' tenki ta iya ke; mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ kʉrɨ anɨ iya pʉra na'ne' uya ikupʉ mɨrɨ Itepuru iwano' pe, mɨrɨpan uya tenki ta Papa pɨ'.\x - \xo 14:6 \xt Koro'se 2:16\x*
\v 7 Apʉne pʉra urɨ'nokon uko'mamʉ uiwano' kon pe rɨken pen, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ eri'nɨ uiwano' kon pe rɨken pen.
\v 8 Uko'man nɨ pe iyesi yau, Itepuru iwano' pe uko'man nɨ; mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ eri'nɨ pe iyesi yau, eri'nɨ Itepuru iwano' pe. Mɨrɨ pɨ' si, uko'man nɨ pe iyesi yau mɨrɨ pe pʉra eri'nɨ pe iyesi yau, Itepuru iwano' pe rɨ e'nɨ.
\p 
\v 9 Serɨ wenai kuru si, Kʉrai erikʉ'pʉ mɨrɨpan e'mʉ'sa'ka'pʉ nurɨne te'to' ya', iyeri'sa' kon mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ nurɨne te'san epuru pe te'to' pe.
\v 10 Ɨmɨrɨ si, ɨ'rɨto' pe ɨtonpa eseru aimenka auya? Mɨrɨ pe pʉra, ɨ'rɨto' pe ɨtonpa ewaruma'tɨ auya? Tanporo urɨ'nokon e'mʉ'sa'kasa' e'to' oton Papa uya eseru aimenkato' apon piyau.\x - \xo 14:10 \xt 2 Koren 5:10\x*
\v 11 Iye'menukasa':
\q1 “‘Uko'manyai'ne' kasa,’ ta Itepuru uya,
\q1 ‘Tanporon kon e'sekunkato' oton urau;
\q2 tanporon ani uya ekamato' oton Papa pɨ',’”\f + \fr 14:11 \ft Aisaya 45:23\f*
\m tukai'.
\v 12 Mɨrɨ pɨ' nin si, ukaisarɨ'nokon usekaman nɨto' oton kon Papa pɨ'.
\p 
\v 13 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', utonpa kon amʉ' eseru aimenkato' ereutanʉ'pai'nokon. E'tane ru'ku, ɨusenuminkato' kon ikonekatɨ' ɨtonpa kon e'pi'poto' ipona mɨrɨ pe pʉra iwa'kʉ'nin tʉrʉ auya'nokon namai' ite'ma ta'.
\v 14 Urɨ, Itepuru Sises yau te'sen ye' pe, upona kuru ɨri pe te'sen kiyari\f + \fr 14:14 \fq ɨri pe te'sen kiyari; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq ɨri pe te'sen\f* pʉra rɨ iyesi. E'tane ɨnʉ' uya rɨ ɨri pe ikupʉ yau, ɨri pe rɨ iyesi mɨrɨ ipona.
\v 15 Ɨtonpa e'kʉuma pe iyesi yau ananɨ'pʉ pɨ', usi'nʉnkan nɨto' esi pen nɨ mɨrɨ ɨnkupʉnʉ yau. Ananɨ'pʉ ɨtonpa ma'tanʉ'nin Kʉrai uma'ta'pʉ iwenaino pe rʉ'pʉ.
\v 16 Wakʉ pe ɨnkupʉnʉ kʉse'nin ɨri pe usauro'nɨto' ipɨ' pe.
\v 17 Apʉne pʉra Papa e'to' esa' wannɨ pe esi pen enta'nan mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ensi pe pen, e'tane Papa uya anʉn nɨ ipokena' pe, tʉusewankamai' pʉra mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ pori' pe Wakʉ A'kwarʉ yau,
\v 18 apʉne pʉra Kʉrai tʉrawasooi pe te'sen serɨ kasa esi Papa pori'manin pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ka'pon amʉ' uya wakʉ tato' ipɨ' pe.
\p 
\v 19 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', tʉusewankamai' pʉra e'nɨto' ya' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨsi'kaisa rɨ usemo'kan nɨto' pe apurɨto' yau epika'tɨn nɨto' ya' anin ku'pai'nokon.
\v 20 Papa tʉrawasooi kʉ'ma'tanʉ'tʉu kiyari pɨkɨrɨ rɨ. Tanporon kiyari esi wakʉ pe Papa enu yau, e'tane ipoken pʉra iyesi ka'pon enta'na a'tai tʉron nɨ e'pi'po emapu'tɨnin pe.
\v 21 Wakʉ pe parɨ iyesi o' tanse pʉra e'nɨ mɨrɨ pe pʉra waain tensii' pʉra mɨrɨ pe pʉra ɨ'rɨ rɨ tʉku'se pʉra ɨtonpa uta'mo'ka emapu'tɨnin pe.
\p 
\v 22 Mɨrɨ wenai, mapurɨyatʉi'ne' serɨ ton pɨ' enkurunpatɨ' ɨmɨrɨ'nokon mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Papa ya' rɨken. Pori' pe te'sen kʉrɨ rɨ ka'pon tiwano' pe tʉuseno'masen pen wakʉ tato' tʉuya ipɨ' winɨ.
\v 23 E'tane kʉrɨ ka'pon ikasimanin useno'masa' mɨrɨ iyenta'nasa' yau, apʉne pʉra iyenta'nato' esi apurɨto' iya winɨ pʉra; mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tanporon apurɨto' winɨ pʉra nʉye'ai'ne' esi makoi pe.
\c 15
\p 
\v 1 Urɨ'nokon pana' pe te'san e'to' pe iyesi ɨ'sɨ'mʉnon pokon pe to' uya ikupʉ pʉra iye'to' yau to' pika'tɨ pɨ', iwano' wannɨ pe rɨ upori'manin kon tʉku'se pʉra.
\v 2 E'nɨ na'ne' kaisa rɨ utonpa kon tʉpori'mai' e'nɨto' pe iyesi, wakʉ pe to' ku'nin pe, to' pika'tɨnin pe tʉusemo'kasan pe to' uya apurɨto' yau.
\v 3 Apʉne pʉra Kʉrai rɨ nɨrɨ uya tʉpori'manin ku'sa' pʉra iyesi, e'tane iye'menukasa' na'ne' kasa: “Asapemato' asapemanin nan uya uta'mo'kasa' man upona,”\f + \fr 15:3 \ft Eren 69:9\f* tasa'.
\v 4 Apʉne pʉra tanporon nɨ iye'menupɨ'sa' na'ne' e'menupɨtʉ'pʉ uyenupanin kon pe, imoronka winɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ iye'menukasa' itekare uya tʉpori'mai', e'ku'nɨto' epoto' pe.
\p 
\v 5 Tɨwɨ Papa imoronkato' pe ku'nin mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ pori'mapɨ'nin a'samʉtʉ yau ɨwesi kon a'kwarʉ ke ɨrepatʉu Kʉrai Sises pɨkɨrɨ ɨwesi kon koro'tau,
\v 6 tikin nɨ nin si itewan mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ inta esii'ma urɨ'nokon Epuru Sises Kʉrai e'to' itese' pɨ' Papa mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Ikʉipʉnʉ apurɨpɨtʉ kon pa.
\p 
\v 7 Ɨtonpa kon si tanʉnse e'tɨ', Kʉrai uya ayanʉnsa' kon na'ne' kasa, Papa apurɨpɨ'to' ne'nin pe.
\v 8 Ekama uya ɨpɨ'nokon Kʉrai enasa' Esuwerʉ amʉ'\f + \fr 15:8 \ft Kiri' maimu uya \fq itun pi'pɨ iputurʉkasa' ton \ft ta,\f* poitorʉ pe Papa e'to' i'nairon pe ekamanin pe, isauro'sa' rʉ'pʉ iku'to' pe tʉuya tukai' tamokori ton amʉ' pɨ'
\v 9 Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen uya Papa apurɨpɨ'to' pe ɨsentu'ke' pe iyesi pɨ', iye'menukasa' na'ne' kasa:
\q1 “Serɨ wenai ayapurɨpɨtʉ uya mɨrɨ Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen koro'tau;
\q2 eren erenka uya mɨrɨ ɨyese' pɨ',”\f + \fr 15:9 \ft 2 Sanwerʉ 22:50; Eren 18:49\f*
\m tasa' iya.
\v 10 Taka'sa' iya kanan,
\q1 “Epori'matɨ', Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen, imunkɨ amʉ' pokon pe,”\f + \fr 15:10 \ft Isu'taronomi 32:43\f*
\m tasa' iya.
\v 11 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ kanan,
\q1 “Itepuru apurɨpɨ'tɨ', tanporon kon Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen,
\q2 mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ apurɨpɨ'to' erenkatɨ', tanporon kon ka'pon amʉ',”\f + \fr 15:11 \ft Eren 117:1\f*
\m tasa' iya.
\v 12 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ kanan, Aisaya uya ta,
\q1 “Ise'si Atʉ rʉ'pʉ e'mʉ'sa'ka mɨrɨ,
\q2 kʉrɨ te'mʉ'sa'ka ton tʉpataron kon esa' pe te'to' pe;
\q1 Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen e'ku'to' e'to' oton iyau,”\f + \fr 15:12 \ft Aisaya 11:10\f*
\m ta iya.
\p 
\v 13 Tɨwɨ Papa e'ku'nɨto' ipɨ' ɨkupʉi'nokon eke pe kuru pori' pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉusewankamasen pe pʉra tapurɨ auya'nokon koro'tau, ayanʉkʉ kon pa ɨye'ku'to' kon ike ke Wakʉ A'kwarʉ meruntɨrʉ winɨ.
\s1 Paarʉ, Esuwerʉ Amʉ' Pen Poitorʉ
\p 
\v 14 Sapurɨyai' kuru rɨ, utonpa ton, ɨmɨrɨ'nokon esi wakʉ pe kuru rɨ, i'tuto' auya'nokon yau iyenuka'sa' pe ɨwesi kon mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨtonpa kon enupanin nan pe kuru rɨ.
\v 15 Ɨmenukasa' uya 'nokon man enari'mʉra tʉron nɨ ton pɨ'ne, ɨyemiya'pontɨkapʉ kon pe rɨ kanan, Papa uya wakʉ nonkasa' pɨ' rɨ urepa pe,
\v 16 Kʉrai Sises poitorʉ pe e'to' pe Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen iwano' pe use'man tʉrawasomanin eseru yau wakʉ Papa ekareei ekama pɨ', Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen enato' pe Papa nanʉmʉnʉ ton wakʉ tʉtʉsan ton pe, Wakʉ A'kwarʉ winɨ iyekonekasa' kon pe.
\p 
\v 17 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', mɨ pe e'kupʉ Kʉrai Sises yau Papa poitorʉ pe esi pɨ'.
\v 18 Ɨ'rɨ pɨ' rɨ usaurokʉ pen Kʉrai nʉkupʉ'pʉ uporo pɨ' rɨken Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen arɨ pɨ' Papa Maimu awɨron kon pe usauro'sa' rʉ'pʉ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ unkupʉ'pʉ winɨ—
\v 19 ento' ipɨ' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ eke Papa tʉrawasooi meruntɨrʉ winɨ, Iya'kwarʉ meruntɨrʉ poro. Mɨrɨ pɨ' si Surusiran ponsi'kɨ siyarɨ Iriri'kun pona rɨ, wakʉ itekare Kʉrai iwano' ekama pɨ' e'sa' serɨ tanporo kuru rɨ.
\v 20 Wakʉ itekare ɨnekamapai kuru e'pɨ'pɨtʉ Kʉrai i'tu pʉra na'ne' airɨ, ɨnʉ' rɨ nʉtʉkaa'pʉ po amɨ uya namai'.
\v 21 E'tane ru'ku, iye'menukasa' na'ne' kasa:
\q1 “Kamoro ipɨ' auro'kasa' kon pen uya ento' oton,
\q2 mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ etanin nʉ'san pen uya ito'ka'nʉ'to' oton,”\f + \fr 15:21 \ft Aisaya 52:15\f*
\m tasa' iya.
\v 22 Mɨrɨ wenai inke rɨ ɨpiya'nokon utɨ pʉra iyesi usemapu'tɨpɨ'sa' mɨrɨ.\x - \xo 15:22 \xt Ron 1:13\x*
\s1 Paarʉ Ekonekato' Ron Pona Utɨn Pɨ'
\p 
\v 23 E'tane si serɨ ton nono yau e'tʉrawasomato' pʉra iyesi pɨ', mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ inke kuru rɨ wʉipiya tenno'pɨ'se ɨyenpai'nokon e'sa' pɨ',
\v 24 ikupʉ pɨ' nin si ekoneka utɨ a'tai Sʉ'pen pona. Utɨ koro'tau ɨpiya'nokon upika'tɨ kon pa utɨto' yau, mɨrɨ yau uyewakiri pe rɨ aka'ne' pe rɨ ɨpokon pe esi tʉpo.
\v 25 E'tane pʉra rɨ, utɨ si serɨ Surusiran pona wakʉ ton mɨrɨ yawon kon apiyo' pe.\x - \xo 15:25 \xt 1 Koren 16:1-4\x*
\v 26 Apʉne pʉra Ma'sitoniya mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ A'kaya pon kon esi'pʉ pori' pe entu'manin nan wakʉ ton koro'tawon kon Surusiran pon kon pika'tɨ tʉuya'nokon pɨ'.
\v 27 Pori' pe rɨ to' esi'pʉ ikupʉ tʉuya'nokon pɨ', to' uya iku'to' pe rɨ iyesi to' iwano' pe. Apʉne pʉra Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen uya Esuwerʉ amʉ' neporonʉ iya'kwarʉ pe te'sen wakʉ rɨ eposa' pe iyesi yau, to' uya kuru rɨ iku'to' pe iyesi Esuwerʉ amʉ' pokon pe rɨ non pon wakʉ rɨ tiwano' kon ekanto' pe iyesi.\x - \xo 15:27 \xt 1 Koren 9:11\x*
\v 28 Serɨ si tʉrawaso enuka'nʉ'sa' uya tʉpo mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ to' uya si tʉneporonʉ kon eposa' ene tʉpo, utɨ si mɨrɨ Sʉ'pen pona utɨ pe ɨyenei'ma'nokon.
\v 29 Si'tuyai', uye'sa' a'tai ɨpiya'nokon, uyepʉ mɨrɨ eke pe kuru Kʉrai uya ɨpʉremasa' kon esa' pe.
\p 
\v 30 Ɨyekama'po uya 'nokon kuru, utonpa ton, urɨ'nokon epuru Sises Kʉrai mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Iya'kwarʉ usi'nʉnkato' winɨ, e'suranmato' yau tikin nɨ upokon pe ɨyena kon i'se esi, upona Papa pɨ' ɨwɨpʉrema kon yau.
\v 31 Ɨpʉrematɨ' apurɨnin nan pen Isutiya pon kon enapai emo'kato' pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Surusiran po e'tʉrawasomato' e'to' pe wakʉ ton mɨrɨ yawon kon nanʉmʉnʉ pe.
\v 32 Mɨrɨ a'tai si Papa eseru pe iyesi pɨ' uye'to' pe ɨpiya'nokon pori' pe ɨpokon pe e'se'na.
\v 33 Papa, usewankaman nɨto' pʉn nɨ nesii tanporo ɨpiyau'nokon. Amen.
\c 16
\s1 Tʉmɨrɨ Pe Rɨ Nin Si Miyarɨ Tato' Iya
\p 
\v 1 Ɨpɨ'nokon ina parusi Pepi ekama uya, so'si Senkʉre yawon poitorʉ pe te'sen.\f + \fr 16:1 \fq poitorʉ; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq uri'san so'si epuru pika'tɨnin\f*
\v 2 Ɨyekama'po uya 'nokon Itepuru awɨrɨ anʉmʉ kon pa wakʉ ton anʉnto' eseru yau mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨ'rɨ rɨ i'se iye'to' ɨwinɨpaino kon ke ipika'tɨtɨ', apʉne pʉra eke pe rɨ tu'kan kon nɨ ka'pon amʉ' pika'tɨnin kʉrɨ rɨ, urɨ rɨ to' tonpa pe.
\li1 
\v 3 Miyarɨ ka'tɨ' Pʉre'sira\f + \fr 16:3 \ft Kiri' maimu uya \fq Pʉresʉ'ka \ft ta.\f* mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ A'kira pɨ', e'tʉrawasoma Kʉrai Sises yau tonpa ton pɨ'.\x - \xo 16:3 \xt Inkupʉ'pʉ 18:2\x*
\v 4 Tʉuma'tato' kon annau rɨ upika'tɨ'pʉ to' uya. Urɨ rɨken pen e'tane tanporon nɨ so'si ton Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen iwano' ton esi pori' pe to' pɨ'.
\li1 
\v 5 Miyarɨ ka'tɨ' rɨ marɨ so'si to' iwʉ' tau tamʉrasan pɨ'.
\li1 Miyarɨ ka'tɨ' utonpa rʉ'kwɨ Epene'tos pɨ', wapiya kuru iyera'tɨsa' rʉ'pʉ Kʉrai winɨkʉi' Eisa nono po.
\li1 
\v 6 Miyarɨ ka'tɨ' Meri pɨ', sa'man pe kuru ɨiwano' kon pe iye'tʉrawasomasa' rʉ'pʉ.
\li1 
\v 7 Miyarɨ ka'tɨ' Antʉroni'kas mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Isuniyas,\f + \fr 16:7 \fq Isuniyas; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra \fq Isuniya; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra \fq Isuriya \ft —uri'san pe iyesi'pʉ ta e'kwa pe.\f* utonpa ton, upokon pe pariki'si tau iye'sa' kon. Eke ton pe kuru itekare ekamai' enno'sa' kon koro'tau te'san kamoro, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ urawɨrɨ Kʉrai yau to' esi'pʉ.
\li1 
\v 8 Miyarɨ ka'tɨ' Anpʉriya'tas pɨ', Itepuru yau uni'nʉnkanʉ.
\li1 
\v 9 Miyarɨ ka'tɨ' Orʉpanos pɨ', Kʉrai yau e'tʉrawasoman tonpa, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ utonpa rʉ'kwɨ Sʉ'ta'kes.
\li1 
\v 10 Miyarɨ ka'tɨ' A'peres pɨ', wakʉ ye' pe Kʉrai yau i'tusa'.
\li1 Miyarɨ ka'tɨ' Arestoporos tonpa ton pɨ'.
\li1 
\v 11 Miyarɨ ka'tɨ' utonpa, Esuwerʉ pe te'sen Eratiyan pɨ'.
\li1 Miyarɨ ka'tɨ' Narʉsisas amʉtʉ pe te'san pɨ', Itepuru yawon kon.
\li1 
\v 12 Miyarɨ ka'tɨ' Tʉrai'pina mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Tʉrai'posa pɨ', kamoro uri'sami'si amʉ' sa'man pe rɨ te'tʉrawasomasan Itepuru apiyo' pe.
\li1 Miyarɨ ka'tɨ' utonpa rʉ'kwɨ Pɨrʉses pɨ', kʉrɨ rɨ kanan uri'san sa'man pe kuru rɨ iye'tʉrawasomasa' Itepuru apiyo' pe.
\li1 
\v 13 Miyarɨ ka'tɨ' Ru'pos pɨ', anʉnsa' Itepuru iwano' pe, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ isan, usan pe rɨ kanan iye'sa' rʉ'pʉ.\x - \xo 16:13 \xt Ma' 15:21\x*
\li1 
\v 14 Miyarɨ ka'tɨ' Asenkʉri'tas, Pʉrekon, Ɨrʉmes, Pa'tʉropas, Ɨrʉmas mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tonpa ton amʉ', to' piyau na'ne' nan pɨ'.
\li1 
\v 15 Miyarɨ ka'tɨ' Pirorokas, Isuriya, Nereyas mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ iparusi, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Orenpas mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tanporo wakʉ ton to' piyau na'ne' nan.
\li1 
\v 16 Miyarɨ ka'tɨ' ɨsipokon pe wakʉ eseru yau auta'su'ka kon pe.
\p Tanporon Kʉrai so'sii ton miyarɨ nɨkayan.
\p 
\v 17 Ɨyekama'po uya 'nokon kuru, utonpa ton, kamo e'ta'nʉ'nɨ emapu'tɨnin nan enei'ma ɨwesi kon pa mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨye'mata'nokon awa'kʉ'nin kon tʉnin nan. To' nʉkupʉnʉ esi ɨusenupa'pʉ kon ipɨ' kasa pʉra rɨ. To' piyau ke'tʉu.
\v 18 Apʉne pʉra pʉsamoro rupɨ esi uyepuru kon Kʉrai apiyo' pe pʉra, e'tane tiwano' kon nɨ. Wakʉ pe kuru rɨ tʉusaurokʉ kon ke, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ennakan nɨto' ike ke entu'ma' rɨ te'san ka'pon amʉ' enku'tɨ to' uya.
\v 19 Tanporon kon uya rɨ main awɨrɨ ɨwe'to' kon etasa' man, mɨrɨ wenai ipan pe rɨ pori' pe e'ai' ɨpɨ'nokon; e'tane wakʉ pe te'sen ti'tui' ɨwesi kon i'se e'ai', mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨri ku'nin nan ye' pe pʉra.
\p 
\v 20 Papa usewankaman nɨto' pʉn nɨ uya Se'tan\f + \fr 16:20 \fq Se'tan\ft —Makoi ese' isakon, \fq Papa eseru ewaruma'tɨnin \ft ta e'kwa pe.\f* amo'korokʉ mɨrɨ a'ta kon o'no.
\p Uyepuru kon Sises uya wakʉ nonkasa' nesii ɨpiyau'nokon.\f + \fr 16:20 \ft Tʉron nɨ ton imenukasa' ton uya serɨ airon nonkasa'.\f*
\p 
\v 21 Temu'ti, e'tʉrawasoma tonpa man miyarɨ ta pɨ' ɨpɨ'nokon, Rusiyas rɨ, Ise'sʉn mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ So'sipa'tɨrʉ, utonpa ton.\x - \xo 16:21 \xt Inkupʉ'pʉ 16:1\x*
\p 
\v 22 Urɨ, Tɨrʉ'tiyas, kareta menukanin nʉ'pʉ, miyarɨ nɨkayan ɨpɨ'nokon Itepuru yau.
\p 
\v 23 Kayas, tewakiri kon pe urɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tanporo rɨ so'si na'ne' serɨ yau itiwʉ' tau te'san miyarɨ nɨkayan ɨpɨ'nokon.
\p Erastas, eke pata pʉrataai esa' pe te'sen, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ utonpa kon Kuwarʉ'tas miyarɨ nɨkayan ɨpɨ'nokon.\f + \fr 16:23 \ft Tʉron nɨ imenukasa' ton uya v. 24 ke iponantɨsa' se kasa: \fv 24 \fq Tɨwɨ uyepuru kon Sises Kʉrai uya wakʉ nonkasa' na'ne' nesii tanporo ɨpiyau'nokon, Amen \ft ta.\f*
\p 
\v 25 Apurɨpɨ'to' tʉpai'nokon Papa ena'! Pana' pe ɨye'mʉ'sa'ka kon apurɨ auya'nokon yau kupʉ iya, wakʉ itekare sekamayai'ne' kasa rɨ, itekare Sises Kʉrai pɨ' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ama'aino i'nairon onansa' rʉ'pʉ pena rɨ usenpoikasa' na'ne' kasa rɨ.
\v 26 E'tane nin si isenpoikasa' pu'kena' amʉ' nʉmenuka'pʉ awɨrɨ Papa tɨwɨ rɨ tʉuko'mansen uya apiyontɨn awɨrɨ, tanporo tʉpataron kon uya tapurɨto' pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉmaimu awɨrɨ to' e'to' pe.
\v 27 Papa rɨken ta'kwarʉ kenan iwano' pe eke pe iku'to' nesii tɨwɨrɨ rɨ Sises Kʉrai poro! Amen.
